99999998pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We are also pleased to inform you that our business hours are from 8:00 AM until 5:00 PM.</span></p>','2021-01-01 10:06:55','2021-01-01 10:06:55'),(583,'service_categories','title',3,'en','One-day Surgery','2021-01-01 13:57:22','2021-01-01 13:57:22'),(584,'service_categories','slug',3,'en','one-day-surgery','2021-01-01 13:57:22','2021-01-01 13:57:22'),(585,'service_categories','title',4,'en','Inpatient Units ','2021-01-01 14:00:53','2021-01-01 14:00:53'),(586,'service_categories','slug',4,'en','inpatient-units','2021-01-01 14:00:53','2021-01-01 14:00:53'),(587,'service_categories','title',5,'en','Supportive ٍServices ','2021-01-01 14:13:07','2021-01-01 14:13:07'),(588,'service_categories','slug',5,'en','supportive-services','2021-01-01 14:13:07','2021-01-01 14:13:07'),(589,'services','title',6,'en','Heart Center','2021-01-01 15:02:57','2021-02-14 07:57:39'),(590,'services','slug',6,'en','heart-center','2021-01-01 15:02:57','2021-02-14 07:57:39'),(591,'services','content',6,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The heart is the center of human life and one of the most important organs inside the body, which contains many accurate medical details that require a high amount of medical experience, efficiency, responsibility, and speed in making appropriate decisions in some emergencies.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\">&nbsp;</p>','2021-01-01 15:02:57','2021-01-06 21:21:28'),(592,'services','title',7,'en',' Neuroscience Center','2021-01-01 15:07:59','2021-01-01 15:07:59'),(593,'services','slug',7,'en','neuroscience-center','2021-01-01 15:07:59','2021-01-01 15:07:59'),(594,'services','content',7,'en','<p>In the Neurosciences Center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, we offer you a model of an advanced and contemporary medical center, which contains a group of doctors of neurosciences and subspecialties.</p>\n<p>The center also contains advanced and modern medical devices, to provide you with an integrated treatment service that relieves your pain and soothes incurable diseases. The center consists of the Department of Neurosurgery, Spine Surgery, Neurology, Neurophysiology, Sleep Disorders Center, Psychiatry, and Psychology.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our services are distinguished by their combination of dedication and compassion, between expertise and competence, which would provide evidence-based care to meet all patients\' requests and provide them with comfort. We take care of their details and give them our greatest attention!</p>','2021-01-01 15:07:59','2021-03-11 13:13:26'),(595,'services','title',8,'en','Orthopedic Center','2021-01-01 15:12:22','2021-01-01 15:12:22'),(596,'services','slug',8,'en','orthopedic-center','2021-01-01 15:12:22','2021-01-01 15:12:22'),(597,'services','content',8,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The Orthopedic Center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital is one of the largest specialized centers in the area, which provides combined diagnostic and therapeutic services for all cases of bone, joint, and fracture diseases.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Starting from the medical history and diagnosis with the latest magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) devices, through the correct medical intervention and procedure and the necessary drugs, to recovery and follow-up.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\">&nbsp;</p>','2021-01-01 15:12:22','2021-03-11 13:13:08'),(598,'services','title',9,'en','Eye Center','2021-01-01 15:15:15','2021-01-01 15:15:15'),(599,'services','slug',9,'en','eye-center','2021-01-01 15:15:15','2021-01-01 15:15:15'),(600,'services','content',9,'en','<p>The eye center within Almoosa Specialist Hospital is one of the best-advanced medical centers for eye treatment in the region in terms of efficiency, medical equipment, facilities, and services provided to patients.</p>\n<p>The center is one of the leading centers in the field of inter-LASIK operations, treatment of retinopathies, and vitreous surgeries, in addition to performing cataract operations in the eyes, performing vision correction operations, and treating other diseases related to ophthalmology and surgery.</p>','2021-01-01 15:15:15','2021-03-11 13:12:50'),(601,'services','title',10,'en','Obesity Center','2021-01-01 15:21:09','2021-01-01 15:21:09'),(602,'services','slug',10,'en','obesity-center','2021-01-01 15:21:09','2021-01-01 15:21:09'),(603,'services','content',10,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Obesity is considered a common disease of the age due to the change in the lifestyle of young people and children greatly, as they have become dependent on diets full of fat and carbohydrates and low in protein and fiber.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The physical activity limited by the rule of long sitting on electronic devices and not practicing any kind of sport is a reason for this.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>This leads to the accumulation of fats in the tissues of the body and increases the incidence of cardiovascular disease and hardening of the arteries and death rates.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\">&nbsp;</p>','2021-01-01 15:21:09','2021-01-06 21:15:48'),(604,'services','title',11,'en','Women\'s Health Center','2021-01-01 15:29:10','2021-01-01 15:29:10'),(605,'services','slug',11,'en','women-s-health-center','2021-01-01 15:29:10','2021-01-01 15:29:10'),(606,'services','content',11,'en','<p>At Almoosa Specialist Hospital, we care about women and take care of them, so we set up a special section for them on their health. We provide her with reliable medical advice in everything related to women\'s health, from infertility and reproduction problems or problems of menstruation, puberty, and growth, we take care of every detail of female safety through doctors with international accredited certificates from prestigious universities and excellent experience and competence, assisted by nursing staff with extensive experience and high competence in the field.</p>\n<p>The center is equipped with the latest international medical equipment in the field of women\'s health, such as CTG imaging devices, and other modern technologies in the field of obstetrics and gynecology, to provide integrated medical care with a high degree of quality, efficiency, and responsibility.</p>','2021-01-01 15:29:10','2021-03-11 13:12:37'),(607,'services','title',12,'en','Surgery Center','2021-01-01 15:32:42','2021-01-01 15:32:42'),(608,'services','slug',12,'en','surgery-center','2021-01-01 15:32:42','2021-01-01 15:32:42'),(609,'services','content',12,'en','<p>Surgery is one of the largest and most basic departments of medicine that requires a high degree of accuracy, competence and experience, by which it requires a thorough knowledge of organ anatomy and the correct method. Choosing the most appropriate surgical intervention based on the case information and applying it correctly without any errors or complications after the operation is a necessity and requires experience and competence.</p>\n<p>At Almoosa Specialist Hospital, we give the surgery department a great priority due to its great importance and wide applications, by relying on a trained medical-surgical staff who has experience and competence in the field, and is equipped with the latest medical devices and equipment that will provide distinctive health care with a high degree of quality and efficiency.</p>\n<p>Inside and outside the operating rooms, our surgical staff work tirelessly and with a high degree of flexibility, commitment and discipline. The teams that include the anesthesia team, surgeons, nurses, operation technicians and others, starting from diagnosing the disease correctly, assessing the situation and choosing the appropriate medical procedure, whether complicated or simple, there is no objection to our teams, they are ready for everything!</p>','2021-01-01 15:32:42','2021-03-11 13:12:09'),(610,'services','title',13,'en','Sleep Disorders Center','2021-01-01 15:37:17','2021-01-01 15:37:17'),(611,'services','slug',13,'en','sleep-disorders-center','2021-01-01 15:37:17','2021-01-01 15:37:17'),(612,'services','content',13,'en','<p>Sleep is acknowledged as one of the most important vital processes in the human body, which extends to four stages up to its final stage. Any defect or problem in one of these stages may lead to problems and disturbances, which negatively affect human health and productivity. Sleep disturbances are any condition that hinders us from obtaining a good quality of sleep, that may hinder us from practicing our job and daily activities, negatively affect our social relationships, academic, and work achievements.</p>\n<p>Among the most common, sleep disorders: sleep apnea and insomnia, and untreated, may cause health complications, including high blood pressure, tachycardia, and stroke. The symptoms of widespread disorders can be known and identified, through a visit to a consultant specializing in sleep disorders, who will assess the situation and develop a final diagnosis and treatment plan after the examination in the sleep disorders laboratory</p>','2021-01-01 15:37:17','2021-01-08 13:38:20'),(613,'services','title',14,'en','Emergency Center','2021-01-01 15:42:17','2021-01-01 15:42:17'),(614,'services','slug',14,'en','emergency-center','2021-01-01 15:42:17','2021-01-01 15:42:17'),(615,'services','content',14,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The emergency center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital is distinguished by providing various and integrated health services to satisfy the aspirations of its patients and achieve their aspirations.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Our center features specialized doctors who work around the clock, seven days a week, to serve patients and clients, assisted by the latest state-of-the-art medical technology in the field of emergency</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital Emergency Center receives more than eighty-six thousand cases annually and includes several specialties such as internal medicine, cardiac services, obstetrics and gynecology, and general surgery.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>It has been provided with twenty-six beds and several rooms for unexpected deliveries, and a staff of the most skilled consultants and specialists in specialized clinics such as the pediatric clinic, the internal medicine clinic, the obstetrics and gynecology clinic, and general surgery, all operate around the clock.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\">&nbsp;</p>','2021-01-01 15:42:17','2021-03-11 13:11:55'),(616,'services','title',15,'en','Nawal Al-Afaliq Cancer Center','2021-01-01 15:46:59','2021-01-01 15:46:59'),(617,'services','slug',15,'en','nawal-al-afaliq-cancer-center','2021-01-01 15:46:59','2021-01-01 15:46:59'),(618,'services','content',15,'en','<p>The Nawal Al-Afaliq Cancer Center provides full treatment plans and full medical care for people with cancer. Our center aims to decrease cancer diseases in the region by providing medical staff with extensive experience in the field of oncology. He is assisted by the most delicate equipment, modern technologies, and integrated programs in the field of patient care, prevention, and health education.</p>\n<p>At the center, we provide all services related to cancer, including:</p>\n<p>-General check-ups and comprehensive care for cancer diseases in the outpatient department.</p>\n<p>-Inpatient long-term chemotherapy injection (requires only one night\'s sleep in hospital).</p>\n<p>-Rapid chemotherapy injections and blood transfusions (performed in an outpatient short-stay unit).</p>','2021-01-01 15:46:59','2021-01-08 13:34:51'),(619,'services','title',16,'en','Gastroenterology Center','2021-01-01 15:52:13','2021-01-01 15:52:13'),(620,'services','slug',16,'en','gastroenterology-center','2021-01-01 15:52:13','2021-01-01 15:52:13'),(621,'services','content',16,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">In the Gastroenterology Center, we provide integrated medical care for patients, starting with the proper diagnosis of the situation and taking a history of it, through diagnosis using modern and advanced medical devices.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Then treatment according to organized, detailed, comprehensive treatment plans for the appropriate medication and appropriate medical intervention, in addition to periodic follow-up of the case continuously, leading to the patient\'s complete recovery and return to normal life.</span></p>','2021-01-01 15:52:13','2021-01-01 15:52:13'),(622,'services','title',17,'en','Nephrology and Dialysis Center','2021-01-01 15:58:53','2021-01-01 15:58:53'),(623,'services','slug',17,'en','nephrology-and-dialysis-center','2021-01-01 15:58:53','2021-01-01 15:58:53'),(624,'services','content',17,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The Department of Kidney Diseases and Dialysis at Almoosa Specialist Hospital contains numerous modern medical devices related to the field.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The most prominent of which is the (BBRAUN Dialog) devices, which are considered one of the best and most modern dialysis techniques in the world, as they are characterized by high efficiency, ease of use, and complete safety. They are also equipped with a large screen that monitors all indicators during the washing session, including the indicator for automatic blood pressure measurement.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">This new generation of hemodialysis machines is characterized by its ability to measure the dialysis dose throughout the treatment period, with advanced technologies that enable the doctor to define and adjust the treatment parameters precisely, which helps to reach the maximum effectiveness of dialysis.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">BBRAUN works with a new method called Hemodiafiltration via the Internet, which removes toxins and large particles from the blood, which was impossible to do with traditional dialysis methods.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">In addition, the center contains other advanced devices such as CRRT devices, which are among the latest technologies for kidney replacement. </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">These devices can wash the kidneys of patients who suffer from severe diseases in the intensive care unit, such as low blood pressure and sepsis.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\">&nbsp;</p>','2021-01-01 15:58:53','2021-03-11 13:11:32'),(625,'services','title',18,'en','Pediatric Center','2021-01-01 16:02:50','2021-01-01 16:02:50'),(626,'services','slug',18,'en','pediatric-center','2021-01-01 16:02:50','2021-01-01 16:02:50'),(627,'services','content',18,'en','<p>Children are the bright side in the life of parents; it is around them that the lives and concerns of the parents revolve around them. Therefore, the health of our children is a priority for the parents as it is our priority also in the pediatric center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital. The hospital is one of the most comprehensive care centers for children in the region</p>','2021-01-01 16:02:50','2021-03-11 13:11:04'),(628,'services','title',19,'en','Ear, Nose, and Throat Center','2021-01-01 16:07:20','2021-01-01 16:07:20'),(629,'services','slug',19,'en','ear-nose-and-throat-center','2021-01-01 16:07:20','2021-01-01 16:07:20'),(630,'services','content',19,'en','<p>The Department of Otolaryngology specializes in the complete diagnosis and treatment of neck damages and head diseases. Our medical staff consisting of surgeons, audiologists, and speaking difficulties experts are all highly trained to treat all kinds of otolaryngology.</p>\n<p>Our available treatments, whether medical or surgical, range from investigations to more complex surgeries for cancerous and non-cancerous tumors of the head and neck.</p>','2021-01-01 16:07:20','2021-01-08 13:26:36'),(631,'services','title',20,'en','Dermatology Clinic','2021-01-01 16:10:54','2021-01-01 16:10:54'),(632,'services','slug',20,'en','dermatology-clinic','2021-01-01 16:10:54','2021-01-01 16:10:54'),(633,'services','content',20,'en','<p>The Dermatology Clinic at Almoosa Specialist Hospital offers a wide range of curative and cosmetic services. Our medical staff is trained to respond to all the needs of our patients with full compassion and full respect for their privacy and human dignity. Therefore, dermatology clinics are uniquely designed to ensure privacy and comfort for our patients. It also equipped with the latest in cosmetic and treatment science tools and medical technologies.</p>','2021-01-01 16:10:54','2021-03-11 13:10:47'),(634,'services','title',21,'en','Family Medicine Clinic','2021-01-01 16:13:22','2021-01-01 16:13:22'),(635,'services','slug',21,'en','family-medicine-clinic','2021-01-01 16:13:22','2021-01-01 16:13:22'),(636,'services','content',21,'en','<p>In a healthcare system, that is getting more and more complex, caring for patients becomes difficult and limited. From here comes our role &ndash; we, the family medicine clinic - at Almoosa Specialist Hospital to provide integrated and continuous health care in which the focus is on the individual as a human being with his details that we take care of, with all his distinctive human makeup of spirit, mind, and body.</p>\n<p>We believe that the relationship between the doctor and the patient is the basis on which the principle of patient-centered care is based by using evidence-based medicine, and we aim to provide you with the best and latest health care in the region.</p>\n<p>Being &ldquo;prevention is better than cure&rdquo;, we invite you to visit us - whether you are sick or healthy - to carry out the necessary medical examinations for you, which will help you determine the extent of your physical health with high accuracy. In addition, guide you to sound medical advice to maintain a healthy body free from diseases and ailments.</p>','2021-01-01 16:13:22','2021-03-11 13:10:30'),(637,'services','title',22,'en','Respiratory Diseases Clinic','2021-01-01 16:15:14','2021-01-01 16:15:14'),(638,'services','slug',22,'en','respiratory-diseases-clinic','2021-01-01 16:15:14','2021-01-01 16:15:14'),(639,'services','content',22,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The respiratory system is one of the basic organs in the human body, and diseases related to it are among the most common. By virtue of human life in the modern era, ambient air pollution, and the spread of radioactive materials.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">In the Respiratory Diseases Clinic at Al Moosa Specialist Hospital, we provide diagnostic and treatment services for patients suffering from diseases related to lung and breathing. Our medical staff has long experience in treating a wide range of respiratory diseases: asthma, emphysema, pulmonary fibrosis, and lung cancer. Our respiratory doctors work in a team spirit with radiologists, thoracic surgeons, pathologists, and more&hellip; to provide the most accurate diagnoses and treatment options using the latest medical tools and tools.</span></p>','2021-01-01 16:15:14','2021-01-01 16:15:14'),(640,'services','title',23,'en','Plastic Surgery Clinic','2021-01-01 16:18:53','2021-01-01 16:18:53'),(641,'services','slug',23,'en','plastic-surgery-clinic','2021-01-01 16:18:53','2021-01-01 16:18:53'),(642,'services','content',23,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Plastic surgery is one of the most important and widespread surgeries in our modern time, as the human being always seeks beauty and distinction by keeps up with the latest modern cosmetic technologies.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">We have established a plastic surgery clinic at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital equipped with the latest modern medical devices and a team of highly qualified and experienced doctors. The plastic surgery clinic at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital is one of the most prestigious integrated and advanced plastic surgery clinics in Al-Ahsaa. We are keen to treat our patients with all professionalism and care, knowing that they have placed their trust in us to beautify their appearance and take care of their health. <strong>Choose us with confidence</strong>, we care about your details and preserve your beauty.</span></p>','2021-01-01 16:18:53','2021-01-01 16:18:53'),(643,'services','title',24,'en','Vascular Surgery Clinic','2021-01-01 16:20:43','2021-01-06 21:28:12'),(644,'services','slug',24,'en','vascular-surgery-clinic','2021-01-01 16:20:43','2021-01-06 21:28:12'),(645,'services','content',24,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The Vascular Surgery Clinic at Al-Moosa Hospital provides diagnostic and treatment services for arterial and venous problems, some of which are done without surgical intervention using the laser, and the other is using surgery.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The department includes highly qualified medical competencies, as it is considered one of the unique specialties in the entire eastern region, which performs many surgeries in various branches of specialization with the best possible results.</span></p>','2021-01-01 16:20:43','2021-01-01 16:20:43'),(646,'services','title',25,'en',' Urology Clinic','2021-01-01 16:24:07','2021-01-01 16:24:07'),(647,'services','slug',25,'en','urology-clinic','2021-01-01 16:24:07','2021-01-01 16:24:07'),(648,'services','content',25,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">In the Urology Unit at Al Moosa Specialist Hospital, we provide general care related to a wide and complex range of urinary problems. Our experts are fully committed to preserving patient privacy and providing the highest quality of care and comfort. Our clinic is equipped with the latest equipment and the best endoscopic techniques that enable our medical staff to achieve the highest results in treating urological diseases.</span></p>','2021-01-01 16:24:07','2021-01-01 16:24:07'),(649,'services','title',26,'en','Diabetes and Endocrinology Center','2021-01-01 16:27:49','2021-01-01 16:27:49'),(650,'services','slug',26,'en','diabetes-and-endocrinology-center','2021-01-01 16:27:49','2021-01-01 16:27:49'),(651,'services','content',26,'en','<p>Diabetes is one of the fastest-growing health problems in the world, and the number of people with it has reached a very large percentage in Saudi Arabia.</p>\n<p>This is mainly due to the problem of obesity, lack of exercise, and unhealthy eating habits represented by long sitting in front of laptops and mobile phones, in addition to eating at night and other habits. Recent studies indicate that the expected number in 2030 of people with diabetes will reach more than two million. It is expected that eighty percent of these cases will be due to problems related to obesity.</p>','2021-01-01 16:27:49','2021-01-08 13:20:36'),(652,'service_sections','title',4,'en','Outpatient Heart clinics ','2021-01-01 16:35:35','2021-01-01 16:35:35'),(653,'service_sections','title',5,'en','Cardiothoracic Surgery for Adults and Children','2021-01-01 16:36:16','2021-01-01 16:36:16'),(654,'service_sections','title',6,'en','Cardiac Catheterization','2021-01-01 16:37:00','2021-01-01 16:37:00'),(655,'service_sections','title',7,'en','Why do you choose the heart center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital?','2021-01-01 16:37:58','2021-03-11 13:01:45'),(656,'service_section_items','title',8,'en','Outpatient Heart Clinics ','2021-01-01 16:40:40','2021-01-01 16:40:40'),(657,'service_section_items','content',8,'en','<p>The external clinics provide comprehensive services for all the cardiac patients who need a full evaluation of their condition and constant care We also offer non-interventional cardiac services for adults and children:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Transthoracic Echo (TTE)</li>\n<li>Transesophageal Echo (TEE)</li>\n<li>Cardiac MRI.</li>\n<li>Nuclear diagnostic imaging (Myoview scan)&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Dobutamine Stress Echo.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Holter Monitoring.</li>\n<li>Digital Blood Pressure Monitoring.</li>\n</ul>','2021-01-01 16:40:40','2021-02-16 17:41:32'),(658,'service_section_items','title',9,'en','Cardiothoracic Surgery for Adults and Children','2021-01-01 16:42:13','2021-01-01 16:42:13'),(659,'service_section_items','content',9,'en','<p>Our center provides invasive and non-invasive surgical options for our adults and pediatric patients. It is considered one of the most distinctive services of the center. It requires experience and appropriate decisions making skills. Services offered:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pulmonary valve balloon valvoplasty.</li>\n<li>Aortic valve balloon valvoplasty.</li>\n<li>Invasive and noninvasive atrial septal defect closure.</li>\n<li>Invasive and noninvasive ventricular septal defect closure.</li>\n<li>PDA closure.</li>\n<li>ASD closure.</li>\n<li>Coaractation repair.</li>\n<li>Minimum invasive heart valve repair or replacement.</li>\n<li>Coronary artery bypass surgery -Cardiac tumors surgical removal.</li>\n<li>Surgical treatment of heart arrhythmia.</li>\n</ul>','2021-01-01 16:42:13','2021-02-16 17:52:27'),(660,'service_section_items','title',10,'en','Cardiac Catheterization','2021-01-01 16:48:37','2021-01-01 16:48:37'),(661,'service_section_items','content',10,'en','<p>Cardiac catheterization is a medical procedure used to diagnose and treat heart conditions. It helps us take a close look at the heart to identify problems and perform other tests or procedures on your heart.</p>\n<p>Services offered at the Cath Lab:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Diagnose and treat coronary artery diseases</li>\n<li>Diagnose and treat cardiac valve diseases</li>\n<li>Diagnose and treat Peripheral arterial diseases</li>\n<li>Diagnose and treat congenital disabilities for adults</li>\n<li>Diagnose and treat Pericardial membrane diseases</li>\n<li>Transcatheter Aortic Valve Replacement (TAVR) previously called TAVI</li>\n<li>Electrophysiology study</li>\n<li>Temporary Pacemaker insertion</li>\n<li>Permanent Pacemaker Implantation (PPM)</li>\n<li>Defibrillation Cardiac Implantation (ICD)</li>\n<li>Cardiac Resynchronization Therapy (CRT)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The cardiac center is supported with a wide range of services and advanced technologies such as CCU, ICU, PICU, Digital OR, Rehabilitation, and Anesthesia team.</p>','2021-01-01 16:48:37','2021-02-16 18:08:06'),(662,'service_section_items','title',11,'en','Why do you choose the heart center at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital?','2021-01-01 16:51:21','2021-01-01 16:51:21'),(663,'service_section_items','content',11,'en','<ul>\n<li>Multiple Diagnostic and Therapeutic Options for Heart Diseases</li>\n<li>Exceptional capabilities in diagnosing, treating, and following up with cardiac patients through surgical and non-surgical procedures.</li>\n<li>Exceptional Results Our team of specialists and consultants provides the best treatment methods to reach the best results and minimize the recovery period.</li>\n<li>24/7 Readiness: We are here for you, twenty-four hours a day. Our ER department works non-stop and our Interventional Catheter Lab is always ready to receive the cases, within the international standards for the specified time for a catheter interventional procedure.</li>\n<li>Minimal Surgical Intervention: we are committed to provide the safest options using the latest technological methods in treatment to accomplish the best results and to minimize recovery time. All this is performed by elite, well-known doctors, and consultants. Technologies include:</li>\n</ul>\n<p>-Transcatheter Aortic Valve Implantation (TAVI)</p>\n<p>- Rotablator device which is an optimal device to ablate calcium in coronary arteries in most difficult cases through catheterization without the need for surgical intervention</p>\n<p>- Latest methods of treatment for Heart rhythm disorders through catheterization in the cardiac electrophysiology lab which equipped with the latest devices and technologies.</p>','2021-01-01 16:51:21','2021-02-16 18:16:15'),(664,'service_sections','title',8,'en','Neurosurgery','2021-01-01 16:52:49','2021-01-01 16:52:49'),(665,'service_sections','title',9,'en','Nerve Diseases','2021-01-01 16:53:35','2021-01-01 16:53:35'),(666,'service_sections','title',10,'en','Neurophysiology Diagnostic Laboratory','2021-01-01 16:55:29','2021-01-01 16:55:29'),(667,'service_sections','title',11,'en','Mental health and Psychology','2021-01-01 16:56:52','2021-01-01 16:56:52'),(668,'service_sections','title',12,'en','Why choose our center?','2021-01-01 16:59:27','2021-01-01 16:59:27'),(669,'service_sections','title',13,'en','Our Mission','2021-01-01 17:00:15','2021-01-01 17:00:15'),(670,'service_sections','title',14,'en','Our Vision','2021-01-01 17:00:57','2021-01-01 17:00:57'),(671,'service_section_items','title',12,'en','Neurosurgery','2021-01-01 17:03:08','2021-01-01 17:03:08'),(672,'service_section_items','content',12,'en','<p>We perform various types of surgeries for the central, peripheral, and spine nervous system. Our center offers a comprehensive range of procedures and surgeries for patients suffering from disorders that fall within the department\'s services.</p>\n<p>The center also treats some pediatric and newborn disorders, which include (hydrocephalus, spine bifida, and other congenital anomalies that affect the nervous system.</p>\n<p>In addition to post-traumatic conditions including head injuries, spinal injuries, and peripheral nerve injuries, as well as brain and spine tumors, deformities and degenerative diseases and (scoliosis, kyphosis) of the spine, as well as brain and spine deformities, they are some of the most treated disorders in the center.</p>\n<p>We also exceed at our center by assessing the need and benefit of surgical intervention in epilepsy patients. Some cases cannot be treated surgically after studying them, while some cases can be operated on.</p>','2021-01-01 17:03:08','2021-01-08 17:10:04'),(673,'service_section_items','title',13,'en','Nerve Diseases','2021-01-01 17:04:50','2021-01-01 17:04:50'),(674,'service_section_items','content',13,'en','<p>To ensure the provision of high-quality healthcare services to all neurological patients, our outpatient team works with utmost enthusiasm and dedication with patients, their families, and workers in other departments, to provide a patient-centered health service. Our services are based on evidence through continuous assessment of the patient, with the aim of effectively assisting him in treating and managing his health condition.</p>\n<p>The outpatient neurology unit cares for patients with diseases of the brain, spinal cord, peripheral nerves, and muscles who require comprehensive evaluation and regular care. In addition, the services provided by the outpatient clinics to patients are based on the appointment system, in addition to direct attendance to the center in case of patients in need of urgent referrals.</p>\n<p>The consultants in our clinic provide diagnostic evaluation and consultations for the treatment of neurobehavioral and memory disorders, neuromuscular diseases, cardiovascular and movement disorders, headaches, seizures, sleep disorders (obstructive sleep apnea - insomnia), brain tumors, and headaches.</p>\n<p>In addition, many diseases, such as Alzheimer\'s and multiple sclerosis, have molecular immunity. Neurology receives a great deal of attention, good and compassionate care within our center.</p>','2021-01-01 17:04:50','2021-01-08 17:10:57'),(675,'service_section_items','title',14,'en','Neurophysiology Diagnostic Laboratory','2021-01-01 17:07:38','2021-01-01 17:07:38'),(676,'service_section_items','content',14,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Neurophysiology Diagnostic Laboratory</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Neurophysiology is primarily an investigative (diagnostic) discipline that uses computers, electrical, magnetic, and electronic means to record the function of the brain, spinal cord, spinal cord roots, peripheral nerves, and muscles to diagnose functional disorders of the nervous system. These technologies include:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>EEG.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Electromyography.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Nerve conduction study.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Monitoring during operations.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Evoked potential.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Monitoring during operations:</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">It is used for monitoring during surgical procedures to reduce the incidence of neurological diseases during surgical treatments. The goal of this monitoring is to identify changes in the brain, spinal cord, and peripheral nerve function before hard-to-repair damage occurs.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>It is also effective in positioning anatomical structures including peripheral nerves and the sensorimotor cortex, which helps to guide surgeons during autopsies. Surgical procedures using this technique include scoliosis surgery, carotid endarterectomy, and brain resection surgery.</span></p>','2021-01-01 17:07:38','2021-01-08 17:11:26'),(677,'service_section_items','title',15,'en','Mental health and Psychology','2021-01-01 17:13:54','2021-01-01 17:13:54'),(678,'service_section_items','content',15,'en','<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Psychiatry Clinics:</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The psychiatric clinic at Al Moosa Specialist Hospital is considered one of the oldest and most important psychotherapy clinics in private hospitals at Al-Ahsa level. For nearly 15 years, we have been providing treatment to patients from different parts of the Eastern Region and outside as well.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The Department of Psychiatry is pleased to provide psychological counseling, treat all behavioral and psychological disorders, and solve any psychological problem that may face us at any stage and under any circumstance that we face in our life, as we provide psychological and social support through a consultant specialized in psychiatry with a high degree of competence and has long experience In this area.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The Department of Psychiatry, God willing, treats all cases of anxiety, fear, or depression, as well as panic attacks, obsessive-compulsive disorder, sleep or eating disorders such as increased or decreased appetite, or treatment of physical symptoms without an organic cause such as irritable bowel syndrome, migraine attacks, total or hair loss because most of them are Be psychological.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Also, the Department of Psychiatry treats children who suffer from psychological diseases or disorders such as autism, learning difficulties, hyperactivity, distractibility, slurred speech or involuntary urination, or it provides some therapeutic rehabilitation for children and if you have one of the parents suffering from a psychotic disorder such as schizophrenia or volatility Bipolar or a parent with dementia or Alzheimer\'s.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Likewise, the department includes psychologist clinics to provide evaluation, treatment and follow-up services from the use of IQ testing and psychological tests for children and adults, as well as providing psychological analytical therapy and cognitive-behavioral therapy sessions.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The psychiatric clinics team at Al Moosa Specialist Hospital consists of:</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">-Consultants in diseases and mental disorders.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">-Psychologists.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">-Social service.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Depression Treatment Program</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Depression is considered one of the most common psychological disorders in the world, and it is divided into two main types: depressive disorders and anxiety disorders. This disease is spread widely across the globe and greatly affects the mood and feelings of people affected by it. Symptoms of depression vary according to its severity (from mild to severe) and according to the duration of the episode.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">It is (from months to years), and it can be easily diagnosed, and it is worth it for us to know that it differs from the normal feeling of sadness.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">And the stress, and fear that afflicts every human being from time to time in life.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">At the global level, 300 million people suffer from depression, representing 4.4% of the world\'s population, and this is a relatively high percentage. Although depression may affect people of all ages and groups, the risk of developing it is:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">It increases significantly in the event of poverty, unemployment, or upon the advent of calamities and traumatic events such as the death of a close or loved one, or when </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Divorce, physical illness, or problems that may be caused by drug and alcohol use.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>In the Psychiatry Clinic at Al Moosa&nbsp;Specialist Hospital, we offer the complete program and effective treatment plans to control and treat </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Depressive disorders, including:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A complete evaluation and diagnosis of the health and psychological condition.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Tests that would exclude the organic causes of depression. -</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A treatment program developed after a long discussion and dialogue with the patient, and it consists of a treatment plan that uses a drug approach.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Others use psychological therapy (through a cognitive behavioral therapy program or psychological analysis).</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The causes and symptoms of all these diseases and mental disorders have become well known, as well as knowing what happens to the brain from chemical changes in neurotransmitters in every mental illness with the creation of multiple and advanced psychological drugs with an excellent positive effect and avoiding side effects to the maximum degree. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">All this led to a positive surge in the treatment of most Mental illnesses during this period, mental illnesses have become like other organic diseases have their treatments, and thus man lives far from suffering and psychological headache, so there is no need to hesitate, the door is open to return to a life of happiness and hope, God willing.</span></p>','2021-01-01 17:13:54','2021-03-08 19:12:02'),(679,'service_section_items','title',16,'en','Why Choose Our Center? ','2021-01-01 17:17:31','2021-01-01 17:17:31'),(680,'service_section_items','content',16,'en','<ul>\n<li>The Neuroscience Center within Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital is an integrated center that provides neuroscience services (diagnostic and therapeutic), whether surgical or non-surgical, including adults and children, as well as premature babies.</li>\n<li>We provide our services 24 hours a day, as our hospital operates around the clock without tirelessness.</li>\n<li>We provide optimum patient care with a choice of an integrated diagnostic and therapeutic approach using the latest available international methods and the highest standards of quality and clinical research. &middot; We provide long-term health care with high-quality standards for the patient, through a medical staff with extensive experience using the latest modern technologies.</li>\n</ul>','2021-01-01 17:17:31','2021-03-08 19:09:42'),(681,'service_section_items','title',17,'en','Our Mission','2021-01-01 17:19:04','2021-01-01 17:19:04'),(682,'service_section_items','content',17,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">We provide high quality, compassionate, patient-centered healthcare service and care while enhancing the clinical and surgical experience and scientific knowledge of the medical team through continuous education.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">As we always strive to open horizons for multidisciplinary cooperation with the medical and scientific community, we are committed to continuous improvement and achieving growth and development in comprehensive programs, to meet patients\' needs.</span></p>','2021-01-01 17:19:04','2021-01-01 17:19:04'),(683,'service_section_items','title',18,'en','Our Vision','2021-01-01 17:20:10','2021-01-01 17:20:10'),(684,'service_section_items','content',18,'en','<ul>\n<li><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">To be the scout in the field of brain and nerve care, and to become a role model in the field of health service provision in the Kingdom and the Gulf countries.</span></li>\n<li><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The Neuroscience Center at Almoosa Specialist is considered a regional and international center of excellence in the treatment of diseases and surgery of the brain and nerves, as it provides the highest international standards followed in the diagnosis, treatment, and care of patients with brain and nerves in the region.</span></li>\n<li><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The center includes special services and superior skills through a multidisciplinary team, with extensive experience in treating diseases and surgery of the brain, nerves, and spine for adults, adults, and children, including premature babies, where the team uses the latest innovations and advanced scientific methods of treatment.</span></li>\n</ul>','2021-01-01 17:20:10','2021-03-11 12:57:05'),(685,'service_sections','title',15,'en','Services Provided By The Center','20