;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Difficulty concentrating, especially during the day.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Lack of activity and lethargy.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Feeling tired and constantly nervous.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Snoozing while driving.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Extreme difficulty in wanting to sleep.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Constant kicking and kicking while sleeping.</span></p>','2021-01-01 18:49:25','2021-01-08 16:52:40'),(751,'service_section_items','title',40,'en','How are you diagnosed?','2021-01-01 18:50:33','2021-01-01 18:50:33'),(752,'service_section_items','content',40,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The diagnosis begins in the clinic of a sleep specialist, chest diseases, or ear, nose, and throat, where the doctor, after diagnosing you, requests an examination for sleep disorders, and you come to the sleep laboratory after you refer the specialist doctor.</span></p>','2021-01-01 18:50:33','2021-01-01 18:50:33'),(753,'service_section_items','title',41,'en','Pre-examination Instructions','2021-01-01 18:52:26','2021-01-01 18:52:26'),(754,'service_section_items','content',41,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Attendance at eight in the evening to the entrance office.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Take care to turn off the mobile phone during the examination.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The examination is explained in Arabic or English as needed.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Sleep: Do not nap during the day of the test.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Caffeine: Do not drink caffeine or soft drinks on the day of the test.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>PERSONAL ACCESSORIES: Bring your slippers, toothbrush, and a book to read.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Medicines: Bring your medications (long-term medications that you take frequently).</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A companion is recommended for elderly patients.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Personal Hygiene: Wash well before attending.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>It is recommended for men to shorten the hair and trim the beard in the desired places.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Do not use gels and sprays on hair.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>For women, do not apply the gel, hair sprays, or henna.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The examination ends at 5:30 a.m., and you must arrange transportation after discharge from the hospital before coming to the center.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>If you feel tired or have the flu, you must inform the department at least the day before the examination and reschedule your appointment: Call 0135369666 Ext: 1298.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong>Caution</strong>: Failure to comply with the aforementioned instructions may cause the test to fail and difficulty obtaining real results.</span></p>','2021-01-01 18:52:26','2021-01-08 16:53:11'),(755,'service_section_items','title',42,'en','Sleep Check','2021-01-01 18:53:19','2021-01-01 18:53:19'),(756,'service_section_items','content',42,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">During the examination, the sleep laboratory technician puts sensors on different places of the body, such as the head, face, chest, abdomen, and legs, as the sleep disorder device records and measures electrical waves of the brain, breathing movements, oxygen level in the blood and heartbeats, while recording and photographing all limb movements through a high-resolution camera.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>This is done without any pain, the patient stays in a comfortable private room closest to the bedrooms, with all the amenities and public safety, and spends his sleep hours from ten in the evening until the morning, and sometimes some tests may need to be done in the morning period.</span></p>','2021-01-01 18:53:19','2021-01-08 16:53:22'),(757,'service_sections','title',39,'en','Services Provided By The Center','2021-01-01 18:54:16','2021-01-01 18:54:16'),(758,'service_section_items','title',43,'en','Services Provided By The Center','2021-01-01 18:55:52','2021-01-01 18:55:52'),(759,'service_section_items','content',43,'en','<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&bull; Rooms for urgent and unexpected deliveries: designed in a way that takes into account the speed of the situation and the immediate response to the situation</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&bull; Ambulances equipped with the latest modern medical technologies in the field of emergency medicine and ambulance.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&bull; The emergency center is always open and ready to receive all cases and deal with them professionally according to the medical rules applicable in emergency medicine globally.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&bull; Comprehensive emergency services and rapid response to critical situations.</span></p>','2021-01-01 18:55:52','2021-01-01 18:55:52'),(760,'service_sections','title',40,'en','Services and treatment procedures','2021-01-01 18:57:46','2021-01-01 18:57:46'),(761,'service_sections','title',41,'en','The laboratory','2021-01-01 18:58:41','2021-01-01 18:58:41'),(762,'service_sections','title',42,'en','Tissue Pathology Laboratory','2021-01-01 19:17:57','2021-01-01 19:17:57'),(763,'service_sections','title',43,'en','Interventional Radiology','2021-01-01 19:20:02','2021-01-01 19:20:02'),(764,'service_sections','title',44,'en','Endoscopy unit','2021-01-01 19:22:26','2021-01-01 19:22:26'),(765,'service_sections','title',45,'en','Treatments','2021-01-01 19:25:25','2021-01-01 19:25:25'),(766,'service_section_items','title',44,'en','Services and treatment procedures:','2021-01-01 19:29:09','2021-01-01 19:29:09'),(767,'service_section_items','content',44,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Our doctors work together from different specialties to address the immediate and long-term challenges of patients with cancerous tumors. Our compact clinics provide multidisciplinary care in a variety of areas, such as hematology, surgery, laboratory, radiology, pathology, and palliative care. Each case is discussed separately in the Oncology Board Committee, and it develops the optimal comprehensive treatment plans for each case.</span></p>','2021-01-01 19:29:09','2021-01-01 19:29:09'),(768,'service_section_items','title',45,'en','The Laboratory','2021-01-01 19:31:16','2021-01-01 19:31:16'),(769,'service_section_items','content',45,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">He performs various procedures, including biopsy examination of suspected cancer and bone marrow organs, as well as flow cytometry, karyotype, and molecular analysis.</span></p>','2021-01-01 19:31:16','2021-01-01 19:31:16'),(770,'service_section_items','title',46,'en','Tissue Pathology Laboratory','2021-01-01 19:33:09','2021-01-01 19:33:09'),(771,'service_section_items','content',46,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Examines the state of tissue biopsies and surgically collected samples with systematic and very accurate methods of examination (immunohistochemistry)</span></p>','2021-01-01 19:33:09','2021-01-01 19:33:09'),(772,'service_section_items','title',47,'en','Interventional Radiology','2021-01-01 19:35:11','2021-01-01 19:35:11'),(773,'service_section_items','content',47,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Interventional radiology is any precise medical procedure or treatment that is performed by guiding medical imaging methods such as x-rays, CT scans, or magnetic resonance imaging. Most of these operations are carried out through small openings in the body. An expert in the field of interventional radiology can use modern medical equipment (such as medical catheters) that are accurate and are seen inside the body and guided by using different radiography methods until they reach the location of the disease problem and treat it without resorting to surgical intervention.</span></p>','2021-01-01 19:35:11','2021-01-01 19:35:11'),(774,'service_section_items','title',48,'en','Endoscopy Unit','2021-01-01 19:36:13','2021-01-01 19:36:13'),(775,'service_section_items','content',48,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Including GI endoscopes and other types of endoscopes, one of the most popular and successful methods of taking tissue samples (biopsy) and presenting them to specialists in the center in order to analyze the results, review them and provide appropriate treatment.</span></p>','2021-01-01 19:36:13','2021-01-01 19:36:13'),(776,'service_section_items','title',49,'en','Treatments','2021-01-01 19:38:11','2021-01-01 19:38:11'),(777,'service_section_items','content',49,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The Nawal Al-Afaliq Center within Almoosa Specialist Hospital offers a range of treatments for oncological diseases in accordance with existing international medical standards and the latest findings of modern medicine such as:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Antineoplastic:</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Including chemotherapy, hormonal therapy, targeted therapy as pre-operative neoadjuvant therapy as an adjunct before necessary surgical interventions, palliative therapy, and pain care.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Take a tissue sample:</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Taking a sample of bone tissue and organs affected by cancer (biopsy), analyzing it by specialists, and providing the necessary treatment.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Tumor surgery:</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Cancerous tumor surgery, including laparoscopic and reconstructive surgery, and surgical removal of cancerous tumors, is supervised by a distinguished, qualified, qualified, and highly experienced surgical team in the field of oncology surgery.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Transfusion of blood or its components:</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">In some cases, doctors may have to transfuse blood or some of its components. We at the Nawal Al-Afaliq Center inside Almoosa Specialist Hospital provide you with this process, according to the highest safety and sterilization procedures followed globally.</span></p>','2021-01-01 19:38:11','2021-03-11 12:58:49'),(778,'service_sections','title',46,'en','Diseases treated by the center','2021-01-01 19:39:31','2021-01-01 19:39:31'),(779,'service_sections','title',47,'en','Diagnosis and treatment','2021-01-01 19:40:07','2021-01-01 19:40:07'),(780,'service_section_items','title',50,'en','Diseases Treated By The Center','2021-01-01 19:42:17','2021-01-08 16:44:32'),(781,'service_section_items','content',50,'en','<ul>\n<li>Liver diseases.</li>\n<li>Inflammation of the small and large intestine.</li>\n<li>Gastrointestinal ulcers, whether in the intestine or stomach, are treated after knowing their causes.</li>\n<li>Cases of gastro-esophageal reflux and heartburn.</li>\n<li>Colic polyps and related diseases.</li>\n<li>Gastrointestinal cancer and treatment plans.</li>\n<li>Diarrhea, constipation, and colon problems.</li>\n<li>Obesity, overweight and nutritional problems.</li>\n<li>Liver and pancreatic diseases and stones inside the bile ducts.</li>\n</ul>','2021-01-01 19:42:17','2021-01-08 16:44:32'),(782,'service_section_items','title',51,'en','Diagnosis and treatment','2021-01-01 19:43:16','2021-01-01 19:43:16'),(783,'service_section_items','content',51,'en','<p>Our doctors in the Abdominal Diseases Center have extensive experience in diagnosing and treating the most serious cases, they are assisted in this by the latest advanced laparoscopes to conduct minimally invasive operations and examinations, such as:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Diagnostic and therapeutic gastroscopy&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Diagnostic and therapeutic colonoscopy</li>\n<li>Stomach balloon installation</li>\n<li>Esophageal stents</li>\n<li>Ligation of the esophageal veins</li>\n<li>Diagnostic and treatment of biliary and pancreatic duct endoscopy, with biliary stents.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In addition, treatment of plasma clots using Argon, which is a medical procedure used to control the bleeding of some cells inside the gastrointestinal tract and to detect tumors within it without surgical interventions.</p>','2021-01-01 19:43:16','2021-01-08 16:45:45'),(784,'service_sections','title',48,'en','About The Center','2021-01-01 19:44:52','2021-01-01 19:44:52'),(785,'service_section_items','title',52,'en','About The Center','2021-01-01 19:46:19','2021-01-01 19:46:19'),(786,'service_section_items','content',52,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The Department of Kidney Diseases and Dialysis at Almoosa Specialist Hospital contains numerous modern medical devices related to the field.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>The most prominent of which is the (BBRAUN Dialog) devices, which are considered one of the best and most modern dialysis techniques in the world, as they are characterized by high efficiency, ease of use, and complete safety. They are also equipped with a large screen that monitors all indicators during the washing session, including the indicator for automatic blood pressure measurement.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">This new generation of hemodialysis machines is characterized by its ability to measure the dialysis dose throughout the treatment period, with advanced technologies that enable the doctor to define and adjust the treatment parameters precisely, which helps to reach the maximum effectiveness of dialysis.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">BBRAUN works with a new method called Hemodiafiltration via the Internet, which removes toxins and large particles from the blood, which was impossible to do with traditional dialysis methods.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">In addition, the center contains other advanced devices such as CRRT devices, which are among the latest technologies for kidney replacement.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>These devices can wash the kidneys of patients who suffer from severe diseases in the intensive care unit, such as low blood pressure and sepsis.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">It is also worth noting that the dialysis unit at Almoosa Hospital is one of the largest units in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, as it contains 30 dialysis machines with a capacity of 120 patients. Each patient has a unique space to ensure privacy and reduce the possibility of infection.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The dialysis unit is based on a team of skilled consultants and specialists in nephrology and dialysis. We also have in the unit a professional technical staff and nurses who are fully trained in the field of dialysis.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>We strive to achieve the principle of comprehensive medical care that makes the patient the focus of his attention, and from here, we have provided the center with clinical dietitians and social workers who collaborate in one team.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The team is tasked with making the rounds to provide patients with necessary information about their diet and to support them socially and psychologically.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The hospital gives priority to hemodialysis patients, as it provides them with dedicated parking in the basement and provides them with private car transportation from their homes to the hospital for free. Finally, we hope that the dialysis unit, with its modern, advanced equipment and integrated staff, will be a distinctive mark and a qualitative addition in the field of dialysis patient care in the eastern region of the Kingdom.</span></p>','2021-01-01 19:46:19','2021-03-11 12:59:16'),(787,'service_sections','title',49,'en','Services Provided By The Center','2021-01-01 19:48:43','2021-01-01 19:48:43'),(788,'service_section_items','title',53,'en','Services Provided By The Center','2021-01-01 19:50:24','2021-01-01 19:50:24'),(789,'service_section_items','content',53,'en',