; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">It does not include any permanent implants</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">A better choice of medication and maintains the urethra and sexual health</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Clinically and scientifically proven safety and efficacy</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">It is one of the day surgeries and can be performed under local anesthesia</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">What is benign prostatic hyperplasia?</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Benign prostatic hyperplasia (BPH), a common medical condition as men age.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">When the prostate enlarges, the layer of tissue that envelops it prevents it from expanding, causing the prostate to compress the urethra, causing the wall of the urinary bladder to thicken and irritate.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The urinary bladder causes pressure, even when it contains a small amount of urine, a phenomenon that causes urination at frequent intervals of time. Over time, the urinary bladder weakens and loses the ability to empty urine. Urethral strictures and partial emptying of the bladder are the causes of a large portion of the problems associated with BPH.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">An enlarged prostate gland can cause uncomfortable urinary symptoms, such as blockage of the flow of urine out of the bladder. It can also cause problems with the bladder, urinary system, or kidneys.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Symptoms of benign enlargement of the bladder:</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Frequent or urgent need to urinate.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Increase the number of times you urinate at night.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Difficulty starting to urinate.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Weak urine stream, a stream that starts, or stops.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Drip at the end of urination.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !suppor