0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The science of surgery is one of the largest and most complex sciences of medicine, as it is a science concerned with the minute details in the human body, so this science is one of the sciences that are constantly developing.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">At Almoosa Specialist Hospital, we were keen to provide a distinguished surgical service through the one-day surgery department, as you can now enter the hospital, undergo surgery, and return home on the same day.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">At Almoosa Specialist Hospital,&nbsp;we are always keen to reduce the length of stay as much as possible, by shifting our operations to the daily surgery department possible, where short-acting anesthesia and advanced surgical techniques are used.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The medical staff, which includes both doctors and nurses, has been trained in the use of health care methods with high training and with a high degree of efficiency and responsibility, which would provide a medical service and health care worthy of the aspirations of our people inside Al-Ahsaa and the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The biggest advantage in the day surgery department inside Almoosa Specialist Hospital is that the patient is admitted and discharged on the same day after only a few hours! </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">However, you have some cases that may require more hours, up to 24 hours, in some operations, as we will notify the patient in advance.</span></p>','2021-01-02 13:38:13','2021-03-11 13:05:30'),(978,'service_sections','title',98,'en','Services Provided By The Department','2021-01-02 13:41:16','2021-01-02 13:41:16'),(979,'service_section_items','title',100,'en','Services Provided By The Department','2021-01-02 13:43:07','2021-01-02 13:43:07'),(980,'service_section_items','content',100,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Within the day surgery department, we perform many distinctive operations with high efficiency and in less than one day only, such as:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Urinary Tract.</span></li>\n<li><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Eye surgery.</span></li>\n<li><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Children\'s operations.</span></li>\n<li><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Ear, nose, and throat surgery.</span></li>\n<li><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Cosmetic surgery.</span></li>\n</ul>','2021-01-02 13:43:07','2021-03-08 18:45:31'),(981,'services','title',40,'en','Coronary Care Unit','2021-01-02 13:51:46','2021-01-02 13:51:46'),(982,'services','slug',40,'en','coronary-care-unit','2021-01-02 13:51:46','2021-01-02 13:51:46'),(983,'services','excerpt',40,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The Cardiac Care Unit at Almoosa Specialist Hospital is equipped with state-of-the-art medical equipment to provide the best possible care for patients suffering from critical heart diseases, including acute heart attacks, acute heart failure, and cardiac diseases requiring intensive care.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\">&nbsp;</p>','2021-01-02 13:51:46','2021-03-11 13:04:46'),(984,'services','content',40,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The Cardiac Care Unit at Almoosa Specialist Hospital is equipped with state-of-the-art medical equipment to provide the best possible care for patients suffering from critical heart diseases, including acute heart attacks, acute heart failure, and cardiac diseases requiring intensive care.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The unit has nine intensive cardiac care beds equipped with German Dragger ventilators and continuous cardiac performance monitors. Our medical and nursing staff aim to provide the best environment for patients by following international health standards. Our doctors and nurses are all highly qualified and work in a team spirit to provide the best healthcare to patients.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">In addition, the hospital follows a very strict sterilization regime in the rooms of the low-care unit, under the supervision of the infection control team, and there is an isolated unit for infectious cases.</span></p>','2021-01-02 13:51:46','2021-03-11 13:04:46'),(985,'services','title',41,'en','Intensive Care Unit','2021-01-02 13:54:20','2021-01-02 13:54:20'),(986,'services','slug',41,'en','intensive-care-unit','2021-01-02 13:54:20','2021-01-02 13:54:20'),(987,'services','excerpt',41,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The Central Care Unit is one of the most important and sensitive departments of Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, as it requires quick and accurate medical procedures, which may be the separation between the patient and his life at times.</span></p>','2021-01-02 13:54:20','2021-01-08 13:04:27'),(988,'services','content',41,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The Central Care Unit is one of the most important and sensitive departments of Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, as it requires quick and accurate medical procedures, which may be the separation between the patient and his life at times.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">We, at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, have given the intensive care unit great attention, after we have provided it with the latest modern medical technologies in the field of intensive care, and a team of doctors and nurses qualified to deal with the owners of the most complex cases.</span></p>','2021-01-02 13:54:20','2021-03-11 13:04:28'),(989,'services','title',42,'en','Newborn Intensive Care Unit and Nursery','2021-01-02 13:56:29','2021-01-02 13:56:29'),(990,'services','slug',42,'en','newborn-intensive-care-unit-and-nursery','2021-01-02 13:56:29','2021-01-02 13:56:29'),(991,'services','excerpt',42,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">There is no doubt that the moments of childbirth are among the most difficult moments in a woman\'s memory, but they are also considered the most beautiful, so there is nothing more beautiful for a woman to feel that a part of her turns into another human being with another spirit.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Sometimes some babies have stressful moments while they are out into the new world due to respiratory problems, congenital diseases, or problems in the birth process, which may make them defining moments in the life of the child and the parents as well.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\">&nbsp;</p>','2021-01-02 13:56:29','2021-01-08 13:05:34'),(992,'services','content',42,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">There is no doubt that the moments of childbirth are among the most difficult moments in a woman\'s memory, but they are also considered the most beautiful, so there is nothing more beautiful for a woman to feel that a part of her turns into another human being with another spirit.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Sometimes some babies have stressful moments while they are out into the new world due to respiratory problems, congenital diseases, or problems in the birth process, which may make them defining moments in the life of the child and the parents as well.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">At Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, we care about these moments and give them great attention. We participate in these difficult moments to be a cause of joy and happiness after the birth of the child and check on his condition and be a hand that helps him out into the new world.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The department of nursery and intensive care for newborns inside Al-Moosa Specialized Hospital is equipped with the latest medical devices in the field of pediatric intensive care, in addition to medical and administrative staff at the highest level of competence and responsibility, since this type of department requires a high degree of focus and speed in making sound decisions.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">There is no doubt that they are difficult moments and cannot be easily bypassed, but with the help of God and with the competence of our department and our doctors inside Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, we help you to overcome them and be a tender hand on your child, to start his journey in life and with him a message that hopes for life is always there!</span></p>','2021-01-02 13:56:29','2021-01-08 13:05:34'),(993,'service_sections','title',99,'en','Services Provided By The Department','2021-01-02 13:57:43','2021-01-02 13:57:43'),(994,'service_section_items','title',101,'en','Services Provided By The Department','2021-01-02 13:59:22','2021-01-02 13:59:22'),(995,'service_section_items','content',101,'en','<p>In the Cardiac Care Unit section, we provide a range of distinctive services related to heart care, provided with high quality and under the supervision of medical staff with a high degree of competence, knowledge, responsibility, and decision-making, such as:</p>\n<p>&middot; Acute heart attacks.</p>\n<p>&middot; Acute heart failure.</p>\n<p>&middot; Post cardiac catheterization services.</p>\n<p>&middot; Post-open heart surgery services.</p>\n<p>&middot; Arrhythmia.</p>\n<p>&middot; Respiratory failure and other respiratory problems.</p>\n<p>&middot; Congenital heart disease.</p>','2021-01-02 13:59:22','2021-01-08 16:03:35'),(996,'service_sections','title',100,'en','Services Provided By The Department','2021-01-02 14:07:23','2021-01-02 14:07:23'),(997,'service_section_items','title',102,'en','Services Provided By The Department','2021-01-02 14:08:30','2021-01-02 14:08:30'),(998,'service_section_items','content',102,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The entire intensive care center was designed by the American company D.I.R.T in the form of separate wings to reduce the possibility of infection and increase the level of privacy and tranquility. Aesthetic details were also taken into account in the design, such as the harmonious colors and landscapes that are usually missing in intensive care departments in hospitals.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">To increase privacy and reduce infection rates, we have made all rooms private and individual, and have designed rooms in attractive and comfortable colors, in addition to allowing natural sunlight to reach each room in order to reduce the level of anxiety and stress for both patients and caregivers.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">A multidisciplinary team of consultants, respiratory experts, and physiotherapists work in the intensive care unit, and nurses monitor patients at a rate of one nurse for every two patients in a smart and innovative way. They are experimental and internationally certified to increase employee efficiency and maintain maximum calm.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">We understand the importance of family and friends in providing support, so, we allow one companion to stay with each patient for 24 hours.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The prestigious American company Stryker uniquely designs the patient beds in the intensive care center, and in each bed, there is a touch screen that enables the patient to control all the functions of the bed through an easy and simple system, and the bed is designed with the highest safety standards so as not to allow falling. In addition, audio materials can be placed in order to calm the patient and help him relax, such as natural sounds and the Holy Quran.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Under the supervision of the Infection Control Department, we follow the most stringent measures to avoid cross-infection, and the unit is equipped with an I360 hygiene system to monitor handwashing compliance among employees.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Among the unique features of the ICU is the presence of CT scans inside the unit, which avoids the hassle of transporting patients outside the unit for imaging, and for the safety of our patients, we have installed monitoring devices in each patient\'s room and nursing stations.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">In addition to all this, every patient\'s case is discussed daily in detail by a multidisciplinary medical team to ensure that the treatment plan proceeds as required, as all ICU procedures are carried out according to the highest international standards based on scientific and practical experiences.</span></p>','2021-01-02 14:08:30','2021-01-08 16:02:04'),(999,'service_sections','title',101,'en','Services Provided By The Department','2021-01-02 14:10:10','2021-01-02 14:10:10'),(1000,'service_section_items','title',103,'en','Services Provided By The Department','2021-01-02 14:15:37','2021-01-02 14:15:37'),(1001,'service_section_items','content',103,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Baby care (newborn nursery):</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Care for healthy babies after birth, and educating parents about newborn care in terms of nutrition, clothes, baby\'s sleep, and everything related to it.</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The Neonatal Intensive Care Unit consists of 24 beds and provides care for:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt 22.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Babies premature from 23 weeks, or babies born with a weight as low as 500 grams.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt 22.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Small size for gestational age.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt 22.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Newborn jaundice.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt 22.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">acute respiratory distress syndrome and other conditions of neonatal diseases.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt 22.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Neonatal sepsis, which is a type of sepsis that affects newborns.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt 22.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Low blood sugar.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt 22.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height