,'<p>Anesthesia procedures are considered one of the medical procedures that have provided a qualitative leap in medical science. After the patients suffered from the pain and pain of the operations for years, they began to perform the operations without any pain after the discovery of anesthesia and its methods.</p>\n<p>We give this medical procedure great attention to make it a point of strength for the benefit of Almoosa Specialist Hospital, as the department uses the most modern medical tools in the world in the field of anesthesia, the department also works with the most skilled doctors with competence, responsibility and medical knowledge.</p>','2021-01-02 14:28:03','2021-03-11 13:03:30'),(1013,'services','content',45,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Anesthesia procedures are considered one of the medical procedures that have provided a qualitative leap in medical science. </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\">After the patients suffered from the pain and pain of the operations for years, they began to perform the operations without any pain after the discovery of anesthesia and its methods.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">We give this medical procedure great attention to make it a point of strength for the benefit of Almoosa Specialist Hospital, as the department uses the most modern medical tools in the world in the field of anesthesia, the department also works with the most skilled doctors with competence, responsibility and medical knowledge.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Our experts assist patients in determining the appropriate method of anesthesia for each patient\'s condition before the procedure, bearing in mind that our priority is patient safety and comfort.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\"