al, and physical condition, we launched, at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, the \"Power of Art\" initiative to embrace various and distinctive Saudi artworks.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">We launched it to encourage works of National art and support for the growing Saudi art in our northern tower, to turn the hospital corridors and rooms into a rich art gallery full of beauty and art, and we offer a therapeutic art scene that enhances the state of surprise and mental alertness for patients, visitors and employees alike.</span></p>','2021-01-03 08:39:01','2021-03-11 13:25:37'),(1681,'community_contents','title',9,'en','The Venue of The Exhibition','2021-01-03 08:40:39','2021-01-03 08:40:39'),(1682,'community_contents','content',9,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">The \"Power of Art\" exhibition will be held at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, specifically in the North Tower - the largest medical tower in the region.</span></p>','2021-01-03 08:40:39','2021-03-11 13:25:46'),(1683,'objectives','title',3,'en','Raise the artistic aesthetic of society by visually satisfying them with paintings and pictures of high quality and artistic value.','2021-01-03 08:43:12','2021-01-03 08:43:12'),(1684,'objectives','title',4,'en','Supporting and encouraging young talents, highlighting local artists, and perpetuating their work.','2021-01-03 08:43:48','2021-01-03 08:43:48'),(1685,'objectives','title',5,'en','Integrating art into the journey of treatment and helping to improve the psychological state of patients, and adopting a comprehensive view that focuses on the patient.','2021-01-03 08:44:32','2021-01-03 08:44:32'),(1686,'participating_groups','title',3,'en','Plastic Art','2021-01-03 08:46:38','2021-01-03 08:46:38'),(1687,'participating_groups','title',4,'en','Photography','2021-01-03 08:47:50','2021-01-03 08:47:50'),(1688,'participating_groups','title',5,'en','Arabic Calligraphy','2021-01-03 08:48:57','2021-01-03 08:48:57'),(1689,'community_contents','title',10,'en',' Why Should I Participate in The Power of Art Initiative?','2021-01-03 08:52:40','2021-01-03 08:52:40'),(1690,'community_contents','content',10,'en','<p>461 works of art from each of the fields of Arabic calligraphy, photography, and drawing participated in the exhibition.</p>','2021-01-03 08:52:40','2021-02-01 19:04:42'),(1691,'community_contents','title',11,'en','“To Learn” ','2021-01-03 09:03:49','2021-01-03 09:03:49'),(1692,'community_contents','content',11,'en','<p>The Director of the Social Responsibility Department in the Ministry&rsquo;s Eastern Province Branch, Khaled bin Ahmed Al-Obaid, expressed his thanks to everyone who sought the success of the &ldquo;To Learn&rdquo; initiative plan, which brought joy and pleasure to the happiness of many targeted families and children.</p>','2021-01-03 09:03:49','2021-02-02 13:02:02'),(1693,'community_contents','title',12,'en','Objectives','2021-01-03 09:05:12','2021-01-03 09:05:12'),(1694,'community_contents','content',12,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The initiative aims to provide 100 computers for the beneficiaries of orphans, needy families and other cases sponsored by the ministry in the Eastern Province, in order to ensure the possibility of completing their educational journey remotely, as Al-Mousa Specialist Hospital provided devices at a financial cost estimated at about (130,000) thousand riyals, believing in its social responsibility and its national duty. Towards members of the community affected by the Corona pandemic, and the Social Responsibility Department was keen to provide devices to male and female beneficiaries to facilitate the distance learning process, and the signing of the agreement was attended by Mr. Abdulrahman Al-Jouf, Director of Public Relations and a number of medical and administrative personnel.</span></p>','2021-01-03 09:05:12','2021-01-04 12:49:19'),(1695,'community_contents','title',13,'en','Cooperation with Productive Families','2021-01-03 09:17:34','2021-01-03 09:17:34'),(1696,'community_contents','content',13,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">We at Almoosa Specialist Hospital believe in the societal role of individuals and institutions within society, because of its great impact on embodying the meanings of unity, interdependence, and love among the elements of society.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Under the auspices of Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, an agreement was made with Al-Bar Charity Society to help some productive families, with the aim of providing a stable source of income that guarantees a decent life for families, reaching the stage of production, self-sufficiency, and improving the economic and social conditions of families.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The initiative is based on the hospital to buy products from productive families, such as the maamoul \"bridges\", which provides hospitality to patients and visitors inside Almoosa Specialist Hospital, in addition to cooperating with a group of families working in the field of sewing clothes to sew a small bag in which the child\'s needs are placed and distributed to mothers as a gift after birth.</span></p>','2021-01-03 09:17:34','2021-03-11 13:26:13'),(1697,'community_contents','title',14,'en','Results of The Experiment and Its Impact','2021-01-03 09:21:19','2021-01-03 09:21:19'),(1698,'community_contents','content',14,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">After implementing the program, 6 productive families were able to benefit from it and achieve good economic income, some of them paid off some of the debts accumulated on it, and some of them achieved their dream of buying a car, and the rest facilitated their economic conditions and reached a good stage of financial sufficiency and the ability to buy the necessary needs of Eid and school clothes And other things.</span></p>','2021-01-03 09:21:19','2021-01-03 09:21:19'),(1699,'community_contents','title',15,'en','The Exhibition \"Health Is A Taste of Art.\"','2021-01-03 09:29:18','2021-01-03 09:29:18'),(1700,'community_contents','content',15,'en','<p>We are keen to provide the best patient experience and all means of comfort and luxury while in hospital.</p>\n<p>The idea of \" Health, the Taste of Art\" arose during the preparations for the grand opening of the medical tower in 2013, for the need to beautify the building\'s corridors with paintings and artworks, here cooperation between Almoosa Specialist Hospital and the Culture and Arts Association was made, and the competition was launched.</p>','2021-01-03 09:29:18','2021-03-11 13:26:23'),(1701,'blogs','title',6,'en','استئصال ورم بالدماغ باستخدام تقنية الملاحة العصبية والمجهرالعصبي','2021-01-03 09:29:53','2021-01-03 09:29:53'),(1702,'blogs','slug',6,'en','astesal-wrm-baldmagh-bastkhdam-tqnyh-almlahh-alasbyh-walmjhralasby','2021-01-03 09:29:53','2021-01-03 09:29:53'),(1703,'blogs','content',6,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility