','<p>Under the auspices of Almoosa Specialist Hospital - General Sports Authority - Saudi Federation for Community Sports.</p>','2021-01-03 09:35:31','2021-03-11 13:26:31'),(1708,'community_contents','title',17,'en','About \"Al-Ahsaa\" Run Race','2021-01-03 09:38:26','2021-01-03 09:38:26'),(1709,'community_contents','content',17,'en','<p>\"Al-Ahsaa Run\" is an annual race organized by Almoosa Specialist Hospital in cooperation with the Public Authority for Sports, which aims to increase awareness of the importance of running and a healthy lifestyle. Sport is the most important method adopted to prevent diseases, as it reduces the deposition of fats inside the blood vessels, and increases energy consumption inside the body, which leads to burning bad fats and reducing the risk of heart disease and strokes. The race is highly popular, with more than 8,000 participants, including adults, children, elderly people, people with special needs, and women. Prizes vary between cars, material sums, and valuable prizes offered to the winners.</p>','2021-01-03 09:38:26','2021-03-11 13:26:58'),(1710,'community_contents','title',18,'en','Treating a Cleft Lip','2021-01-03 09:41:25','2021-01-03 09:41:25'),(1711,'community_contents','content',18,'en','<p>Cleft lip deformity causes bad psychological effects on the child and his family, it may cause severe depressive episodes due to ridiculous bullying incidences, cleft lip procedure is not covered by insurance, and the waiting time may be prolonged in government hospitals. From here came the idea of treating children with this deformity, to draw a smile of hope on their lips</p>','2021-01-03 09:41:25','2021-02-16 17:04:53'),(1712,'community_contents','title',19,'en','\"We Play Together\" Garden','2021-01-03 09:46:27','2021-01-03 09:46:27'),(1713,'community_contents','content',19,'en','<p>We believe, in Almoosa Specialist Hospital in the societal role of organizations and the extent of its success and effectiveness. We also believe in the right of all members of society to receive an equal amount of service, care, and entertainment as well. Therefore, the idea of ​​\"We Play Together\" gardens, which is considered one of the initiatives of Al Muhaidib for community service, was the cooperation between Almoosa Specialist Hospital And Al-Muhaidib Company (<a href=\"https://www.amsf.org/\">https://www.amsf.org/</a>) to establish the first merging garden for children with special needs with their healthy peers, to be the product of a distinguished community partnership between Al-Muhaidib for Community Service and Almoosa Specialist Hospital.</p>','2021-01-03 09:46:27','2021-03-11 13:27:30'),(1714,'community_contents','title',20,'en','Initiative: A Paramedic in Every School \"Everyone is a Paramedic\"','2021-01-03 09:49:52','2021-01-03 09:49:52'),(1715,'community_contents','content',20,'en','<p>Under the auspices of the Life Support Center of Almoosa Specialist Hospital - Education Department</p>','2021-01-03 09:49:52','2021-03-11 13:27:38'),(1723,'doctors','slug',161,'en','dr-batal-al-dossary','2021-01-03 10:12:21','2021-01-03 10:12:21'),(1724,'doctors','name',161,'en','Dr. Batal Al-Dossary','2021-01-03 10:12:21','2021-01-03 10:12:21'),(1725,'doctors','title',161,'en','Pulmonary Consultant','2021-01-03 10:12:21','2021-02-23 08:58:59'),(1726,'doctors','qualifications',161,'en','Specialty: Consultant chest and head of internal medicine\n\nDegree: Holder of the American Board of Pulmonary Medicine, Fellowship of the American College of Chest Physicians, FCCP, Fellowship of the Royal \n\nCollege of Physicians and Surgeons of Canada, FRCP\n\nAreas of Expertise: Has more than 34 years of experience in the field of treating chest diseases\n\nLanguages: Arabic - English\n\nNationality: Saudi\n\nAge group of patients: adults\n','2021-01-03 10:12:21','2021-01-29 16:26:46'),(1727,'doctors','current_positions',161,'en','head of the internal medicine department','2021-01-03 10:12:21','2021-01-03 10:12:21'),(1728,'blogs','title',9,'en','Premenstrual Syndrome (PMS)‏','2021-01-03 10:13:56','2021-01-03 10:13:56'),(1729,'blogs','slug',9,'en','premenstrual-syndrome-pms','2021-01-03 10:13:56','2021-01-03 10:13:56'),(1730,'blogs','content',9,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Ambiguity surrounds the changes that occur to the female before menstruation and the menstrual CYCLE, unfortunately there are lot of misconceptions around that topic, in this article we will try to cover a phenomenon that every female should know and be aware of. Premenstrual syndrome, a term refers to a group of symptoms that afflict a woman about one to two weeks before menstruation (period), and these symptoms vary between physical, psychological and emotional, and these symptoms usually subside and disappear after the menstrual bleeding. Researchers have not been able to uncover the mystery surrounding the causes of premenstrual syndrome, so the most common explanation at the present time suggests that these symptoms come as a result of periodic changes in:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-29314 size-medium\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Female hormones</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Pituitary hormones</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Prostaglandins</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Certain chemicals in the brain (neurotransmitters)</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>From another perspective that should not be overlooked, the lifestyle followed may play a role in the emergence of premenstrual syndrome. It has been found that certain symptoms affect mostly women who:</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Smokes</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Live a life filled with tension and stress</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">rarely exercise</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Not getting enough sleep</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Or those who follow a diet rich in:</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Caffeine</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">salt</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Red meat</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Sugar</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Despite this, the nature of the association of these factors and life habits with premenstrual syndrome is still mysterious, and we still do not know for sure which of it is the definite cause , so is stress and tension, for example, the cause of this annoying syndrome? Or is it the result of it? In any case, what is more likely &ndash; until now &ndash; that premenstrual syndrome usually causes stress and tension and not the other way around. It seems that some drugs may relate as well, as we find that the contraceptive pill causes symptoms of premenstrual syndrome in some women, and we see them lead to symptoms improvement or in others.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">The medical community debates about the difference between premenstrual dysfunction and actual premenstrual syndrome, as most women of menstruation (about 75% of them) share those uncomfortable pre-menstrual symptoms. Despite this large number, one in ten women has symptoms severe enough to the point of disrupting their personal and social relationships, hindering their work, or performing their household tasks. Some doctors consider these severe symptoms to be what should be called premenstrual syndrome. On the other hand, another group of doctors disagrees with this opinion. There is a more severe form of premenstrual syndrome called premenstrual dysphoric disorder (PMDD). A woman is diagnosed with this disorder when she suffers from 5 or more symptoms of premenstrual syndrome, and usually shows mood swings, anger, irritability, anxiety and tension.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Premenstrual syndrome symptoms are divided into two main parts:</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Physical symptoms:</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-29308 size-medium\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Bloating</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Breast tenderness (i.e. increased sensitivity to pain)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Swollen feet and ankles</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Fluid retention and weight gain</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Painful uterine contractions before and during the first few days of menstruation</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Headache</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Cravings for food (especially salty or sweet food)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">acne</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Decreased energy or fatigue</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Palpitations</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Dizziness</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Back pain or muscle pain</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Psychological and emotional symptoms:</strong></span></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Stress</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Mood Swings</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Depression</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Aggressiveness</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Crying spells</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Difficulty concentrating</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Forgetting some incidents</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Changes in sexual desire</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Symptoms of premenstrual syndrome differ from one woman to another, but in most women there are three complaints that top the list: moodiness, fatigue and bloating.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Diagnosis:</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">The doctor usually asks about the following:</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-29316 size-medium\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Your premenstrual syndrome symptoms</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">When these symptoms appear in relation to your usual menstrual cycle</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Symptom regularity (coming monthly, biweekly, etc.)</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Your doctor will also ask you about your general life. Questions might include:</span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Have you been feeling sad, or anxious lately?</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Do you notice mood swings? Or stress? Or difficulty concentrating?</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Are you experiencing difficulties with your spouse, family members, or co-workers?</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Are you in such a hurry that it disturbs your sleep and makes you skip meals?</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Are you living a sedentary lifestyle and not getting enough exercise?</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Do you smoke cigarettes?</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Is your diet high in red meat, salty food, or sugars?</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">After that, your doctor will review your medical history, ask you about any medications you are currently taking, then examine you and, if necessary, perform an examination using a Pap smear. No single physical symptom can confirm a diagnosis of premenstrual syndrome, but a comprehensive examination can help reveal other medical problems, such as hypothyroidism or a tumor in the breast, brain or ovary. This also applies to laboratory tests, there is no single laboratory test that can confirm your diagnosis of PMS, but blood tests help rule out other medical disorders, such as low blood sugar, hypothyroidism, or other hormonal problems that may be present. A cause for your symptoms.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">If your previous test results look normal, your doctor may ask you to keep a daily record of your menstrual symptoms for two or three months to write:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Symptom type</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Symptom severity</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Timing of your period</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Any stress that affected your life during that period. Your doctor will review the record you wrote to see if symptoms appear in a pattern that matches your premenstrual syndrome. Definitely, it cannot be said that the diagnosed condition is premenstrual syndrome if symptoms have not disappeared for about two weeks during the menstrual cycle, as symptoms usually disappear shortly after the start of menstruation until the next ovulation.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>How long would it last?</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Premenstrual syndrome may be a long-term condition for some women, as they experience the aforementioned symptoms beforehand</span></p>','2021-01-03 10:13:56','2021-01-03 10:13:56'),(1731,'doctors','slug',162,'en','dr-mustafa-saad','2021-01-03 10:14:40','2021-01-03 10:14:40'),(1732,'doctors','name',162,'en','Dr. Mustafa Saad','2021-01-03 10:14:40','2021-01-03 10:14:40'),(1733,'doctors','title',162,'en','Infectious Diseases Consultant','2021-01-03 10:14:40','2021-02-23 13:51:25'),(1734,'doctors','qualifications',162,'en','Specialty: Consultant Internal Medicine and Head of the Infectious Diseases and Immunology Department\n\nDegree: Doctor of Internal Medicine and Infectious Diseases\n\nAreas of Expertise: Internal Medicine (Infectious Diseases and Immunology)\n\nLanguages: Arabic and English\n\nNationality: Jordanian\n\nAge group of patients: adults and children\n','2021-01-03 10:14:40','2021-01-29 16:25:27'),(1735,'doctors','current_positions',162,'en','Head of the Infectious Diseases and Immunology Department','2021-01-03 10:14:40','2021-01-03 10:14:40'),(1736,'blogs','title',10,'en','SAVING THE LIFE OF A 29-YEAR-OLD MAN HIS STOMACH MOVED AND SETTLED IN HIS CHEST FOR 7 YEARS','2021-01-03 10:28:57','2021-01-03 10:28:57'),(1737,'blogs','slug',10,'en','saving-the-life-of-a-29-year-old-man-his-stomach-moved-and-settled-in-his-chest-for-7-years','2021-01-03 10:28:57','2021-01-03 10:28:57'),(1738,'blogs','content',10,'en','<h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 64px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Saving the Life of a 29-year-old Man His Stomach Moved and Settled in his Chest for 7 Years</span></h1>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Abdullah, a 29-year-old man, has had a terrible car accident seven years ago, resulted in several injuries in different parts of his body, then he began a long treatment journey and moved between several hospitals where the pain was a companion to him on this journey, he was suffering from acute abdominal pain with recurrent vomiting throughout these seven years.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Abdullah recently came to Almoosa Specialist Hospital in Al-Ahsa, where Dr. Mohammed Al-Awadhi, Gastroenterology Consultant performed several tests, which showed a rupture in the left part of the diaphragm with a large opening through which the stomach, spleen and left kidney moved to the chest cavity instead of the abdomen, where they put pressure on the left lung, that resulted in shrinkage, in addition to a strain on the heart and pushed it to the right side.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Dr. Ayman Ghoneim, Associate Consultant Cardiothoracic Surgery, who received the patient in the Department of Cardio-Thoracic Surgery, said: &ldquo;We held an urgent meeting that included the General Surgery, Cardiothoracic Surgery departments at Almoosa Specialist Hospital,&nbsp; for coordination to conduct major surgery to restore body organs to normal, putting in mind that the mission will not be easy because the length of time led to adhesions between the abdominal viscera and thoracic organs.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Dr. Saeed Abdul-Baqi, general surgery consultant and head of the surgical team who performed this operation said that an opening in the chest was made to remove adhesions between the stomach and the heart membrane, and between the stomach and lung and its pleural membrane, in addition to returning the organs to the normal position in the abdominal cavity and repair of the diaphragm rupture.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">The surgery took almost 3 hours, and it was successful thanks be to Allah. The operation performed through one incision in the chest. After that Abdullah&rsquo;s condition has improved, then he left the hospital seven days later.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Dr. Abdul Baqi concluded that the dangers of such rare cases lie in the ease of injury to the lung, heart or stomach itself, which may lead to bleeding inside the heart or bowel obstruction, which resulted from an injury caused by a car accident seven years ago that&nbsp; not discovered despite his admission to several hospitals during this period, that is one of the rarest cases in the world where most similar cases detected in the first year after the accident, and the world record so far registered one case discovered after five years of the crash.</p>','2021-01-03 10:28:57','2021-01-03 10:28:57'),(1740,'doctors','slug',163,'en','dr-shahin-ahmed','2021-01-03 10:40:47','2021-01-03 10:40:47'),(1741,'doctors','name',163,'en','Dr. Shahin Ahmed','2021-01-03 10:40:47','2021-01-03 10:40:47'),(1742,'doctors','title',163,'en','Internal Medicine Consultant ','2021-01-03 10:40:47','2021-01-03 10:40:47'),(1743,'doctors','qualifications',163,'en','speciality: Internal Medicine\n\nDegree: Doctorate - American Board in Internal Medicine\n\nAreas of expertise: general internal medicine - treatment and diagnosis of shortness of breath - fatigue - chest pain - severe acute disease cases that affect different organs simultaneously - management of multiple chronic diseases.\n\nLanguages: English\n\nNationality: Indian\n\nAge group of patients: adults and children','2021-01-03 10:40:47','2021-01-29 16:24:45'),(1744,'blog_categories','category_name',1,'en','Cardiology Treatment','2021-01-03 10:41:13','2021-01-11 10:30:03'),(1745,'blog_categories','category_name',5,'en','Orthopedic Treatment','2021-01-03 10:43:08','2021-01-11 10:24:46'),(1746,'doctors','slug',164,'en','dr-mohammed-al-awadi','2021-01-03 10:43:48','2021-01-03 10:43:48'),(1747,'doctors','name',164,'en','Dr. Mohammed Al-Awadi','2021-01-03 10:43:48','2021-01-03 10:43:48'),(1748,'doctors','title',164,'en','Gastroenterologist','2021-01-03 10:43:48','2021-01-03 10:43:48'),(1749,'doctors','qualifications',164,'en','Specialty: Gastroenterology and Internal Medicine\n\nDegree: Assistant Professor of Internal Medicine - Doctor of Internal Medicine\n\nAreas of Expertise: Gastroenterology - Gastrointestinal Endoscopy - General Internal Medicine\n\nLanguages: Arabic and English\n\nNationality: Egyptian \n\nAge group of patients: Adults\n','2021-01-03 10:43:48','2021-01-29 16:24:04'),(1750,'blog_categories','category_name',6,'en','Radiology technology treatment','2021-01-03 10:45:19','2021-01-11 11:09:40'),(1751,'blog_categories','category_name',7,'en','Corona Virus','2021-01-03 10:46:14','2021-01-03 10:46:14'),(1752,'blog_categories','category_name',8,'en','Neurosurgery','2021-01-03 10:47:00','2021-01-03 10:47:00'),(1753,'doctors','slug',165,'en','dr-mohammed-tawfik','2021-01-03 10:48:30','2021-01-03 10:48:30'),(1754,'doctors','name',165,'en','Dr. Mohammed Tawfik','2021-01-03 10:48:30','2021-01-03 10:48:30'),(1755,'doctors','title',165,'en','Gastroenterology and endoscopy consultant','2021-01-03 10:48:30','2021-01-03 10:48:30'),(1756,'doctors','qualifications',165,'en','Specialization: Gastroenterology and Endoscopy - Internal Medicine\n\nDegree: Doctorate in Internal Medicine and Gastroenterology\n\nAreas of expertise: Internal Medicine and Gastroenterology\n\nLanguages: Arabic and English\n\nEgyptian nationality\n\nAge group of patients: adults\n','2021-01-03 10:48:30','2021-01-29 16:22:37'),(1757,'doctors','slug',166,'en','dr-ahmed-al-hajjar','2021-01-03 10:51:18','2021-01-03 10:51:18'),(1758,'doctors','name',166,'en','Dr. Ahmed Al-Hajjar','2021-01-03 10:51:18','2021-01-03 10:51:18'),(1759,'doctors','title',166,'en','Gastroenterology and Endoscopy Senior Consultant','2021-01-03 10:51:18','2021-02-22 14:49:07'),(1760,'doctors','qualifications',166,'en','Specialization: Internal medicine specializing in the digestive system and endoscopy\n\nDegree: PhD - Diploma in Subspecialty in Gastroenterology and Endoscopy\n\nAreas of expertise: \n\n* Diagnostic and therapeutic gastrointestinal endoscopy. \n\n* Endoscopic pancreatic and cholangiography, \n\n* ERCP. \n\n* Placing a stent for the esophagus, duodenum and colon. \n\n* Video capsule endoscopy. \n\n* Single and double balloon enteroscopy. \n\n* Laparoscopic gastric insertion tube \n\n* Laparoscopy \n\n* Gastric balloon insertion for obesity treatment. \n\n* pH measurement, esophageal and rectal manometry\n\nLanguages: Arabic - English\n\nNationality: Lebanese\n\nAge group of patients: adults\n','2021-01-03 10:51:18','2021-01-29 16:20:49'),(1761,'blogs','title',11,'en','A VISIT TO A BARBER REVEALS A RARE EGG-SIZED CAROTID SHEATH MASS','2021-01-03 11:09:29','2021-01-03 11:09:29'),(1762,'blogs','slug',11,'en','a-visit-to-a-barber-reveals-a-rare-egg-sized-carotid-sheath-mass','2021-01-03 11:09:29','2021-01-03 11:09:29'),(1763,'blogs','content',11,'en','<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">In a 4-hour-procudere</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Segmented Surgical resection of a large odontogenic fibromyxoma</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Grown up or a kid, we all have Dentophobia!</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The stereotype of the dentist is always accompanied by the feeling of pain or the needle and other unpleasant treatment procedures.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">So, can you imagine if you were misdiagnosed and your visits to the dentist went to no avail &hellip; with ongoing pain!</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Referred from another hospital, our patient visited Dr. Ibrahim Hassoun, oral and maxillofacial surgery specialist, complains of swelling in the lower jaw with ongoing severe pain, she has been treated for a long time but the pain and swelling were the same, as she was misdiagnosed by her doctors who diagnosed her case with a dental abscess.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Radiological examination with MRI, CT, and conventional radiography pointed to a Neoplasm , so a biopsy was taken for further investigation , the result showed that the patient has a large odontogenic fibromyxoma ,a rare benign neoplasm that mostly affects the posterior region of the mandible, that destroyed her mandibular bone</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The medical team that included, Dr . Ibrahem Hassoun , Dr . Hesham Alsayed , and Dr. Dina Abdul Samee agreed that surgery is the treatment of choice for such rare cases , along with placing a Bone grafting from the iliac bone to prevent the recurrence of the tumor</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The surgery that lasted for 4 hours, was a success and the patient was discharged in good health</span></p>','2021-01-03 11:09:29','2021-01-03 11:09:29'),(1764,'blogs','title',12,'en','BOOSTING MEMORY THROUGH DRAWING','2021-01-03 11:16:46','2021-01-03 11:16:46'),(1765,'blogs','slug',12,'en','boosting-memory-through-drawing','2021-01-03 11:16:46','2021-01-03 11:16:46'),(1766,'blogs','content',12,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">It has long been known that drawing something helps a person remember it.&nbsp;Drawing is superior to reading or writing activities because it forces the person to process information in multiple ways: visually, kinesthetically, and semantically</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">The title of a recent documentary film, &ldquo;My Memory Is Better When I Draw,&rdquo; summarizes what research has proven day after day of drawing on cognitive abilities. The film shows how drawing stimulated people&rsquo;s memories with dementia and enabled them to restore their connection with the world. But it seems that this positive effect is not limited to people with dementia, studies have shown that art may be part of treating patients with depression, anxiety, and even cancer, as it allows them to express themselves and their thoughts</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">The practice of art has also been associated with improved memory, critical thinking, and flexibility. In healthy elderly.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Contrary to what you might think, this therapeutic effect does not depend on a person&rsquo;s artistic talent or skills.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Consultant psychiatrist and head of the Neuroscience Center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, Dr. Sherif Saad- Says, &ldquo;Benefit is related to the artistic process and ways to stimulate thinking itself, not the final product or painting.&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">The Healing Power of Art.</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; font-size: 36px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">How Art Heals?</span></h2>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Art is healing because it forces you to forge a connection between your mind and your body. Unlike exercise, which works your body, or meditation, which clears your mind, art-making accesses both mind and body to promote healing. Every time you sit down to write a song or paint a picture, you&rsquo;re using mental processes in a physically engaging activity.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">There is a variety of artistic tools available, from acrylic colors to iPads for people undergoing cancer treatment, and some examples at Harvard University&rsquo;s Massachusetts General Hospital have proven this. The hospital previously worked with former soldiers and Alzheimer&rsquo;s patients; drawing helped them get over their diseases quickly and enjoy their hospital stay.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;Dr. Sherif Saad stated that art has always been able to help people in difficult times, even those who spend most of their free time without specific activities. The doctor adds: &ldquo;Working with a trained art therapist gives patients a way to express themselves in a safe environment, which paves the way for their transition to the next stage of treatment safely. &ldquo;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; font-size: 36px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; vertical-align: baseline;\">The protective effect of art</u></span></h2>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">In addition to the healing abilities of art, this treatment method has been shown to have a preventive effect. Recent research indicates that engaging in creative art practice appears to effectively protect from cognitive impairment more than just an artistic appetite for it. It included people over the age of 70; those who participated in craft projects were less likely to develop cognitive impairment as they age than those who read books.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">A 2014 German study that included two groups of retirees found that the group that practiced painting and sculpture showed more significant improvement in spatial perception and emotional flexibility compared to the other group that attended only artistic classes.</span></p>','2021-01-03 11:16:46','2021-01-03 11:16:46'),(1767,'blogs','title',13,'en','NURSING BETWEEN THE SANCTITY OF MISSION AND THE SANCTITY OF DUTY','2021-01-03 11:26:18','2021-01-03 11:26:18'),(1768,'blogs','slug',13,'en','nursing-between-the-sanctity-of-mission-and-the-sanctity-of-duty','2021-01-03 11:26:18','2021-01-03 11:26:18'),(1769,'blogs','content',13,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">A heart beats with Empathy</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">A blast Hit Lebanon days ago. an explosion that wiped out entire streets across the seaside capital, and left us all heartbroken</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Many stories of heroes are beginning to surface &ndash; and this is the tale of the nurse Pamela who pulled three newborns out of a hospital hit by the Beirut blast</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Pamela says &ldquo;we heard a sound then the explosion happened,&nbsp;I was knocked down unconscious, and when I woke up, the whole place was destroyed .The first thing that came to my mind was the&nbsp;newborn&nbsp;triplets;&nbsp;I ran to the nursery, found the three incubators under the rubble, the babies were safe inside , I started removing&nbsp;rubble and metal rods that fell from the ceiling&nbsp; till I reached the babies, I immediately carried them, I was terrified because the incubators&nbsp;were covered with glass and blood- &nbsp;a glass that used to be widows looking at beautiful Beirut &ndash; the voices of the babies&nbsp;crying reassured me that they are still alive. People were trying to also open for us to leave, they opened a small hole that we left through. My only concern was to protect the babies and get them to a safe place, I went down carrying the three babies with no electricity, I was scared one of them would slip&nbsp;from between my arms, especially that I was shacking from fear and trauma, but the hands of Allah were above our hands. &nbsp;I started running towards the nearest hospital, people started taking off clothes and covering the babies as I ran across destruction hearing my heartbeats louder that the scream around me , the smell of death and the yawning of devastated mothers &rdquo;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">What hidden force that gave her self-control and the ability to save those children!</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">People stand out amidst these violent and dark and these circumstances and this Pamela was up to the task &ndash; how courageous!</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">ASH nurses:</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Hats off to you all, Pamela is an example reflecting the heroism of you, nurses do not necessarily need to save lives in a dramatic scene to be heroes. In many cases, you are caring for patients with compassion when you unknowingly become heroes to the people around you</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Families go home from the hospital thinking about how you made a tremendous impact on their lives. Yet when you are recognized as heroes, you often say you did not do something special. you were just doing your jobs.&rdquo;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">You have qualities that make us astonished, you are not in the shadow , you are &nbsp;the humble leaders and &nbsp;the hope to a better future &ndash; when malls , schools and events were postponed you guys didn&rsquo;t&nbsp; take a break! You risked your own lives to cure patients &ndash; and that is how nurses are meant to be</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Hats off to ASH nurses and all the nurses around the world ..</p>','2021-01-03 11:26:18','2021-01-03 11:26:18'),(1770,'blogs','title',14,'en','SUCCESSFUL AORTIC STENTING FOR A 30-YEAR-OLD PATIENT','2021-01-03 11:29:03','2021-01-03 11:29:03'),(1771,'blogs','slug',14,'en','successful-aortic-stenting-for-a-30-year-old-patient','2021-01-03 11:29:03','2021-01-03 11:29:03'),(1772,'blogs','content',14,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Successful Aortic stenting for a 30-year-old patient</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Our surgical team at Almoosa Specialist hospital led by Dr. Mahmoud Elmeniesy, vascular surgery consultant, managed to save a 30-year-old patient who was suffering from an Aortic dissection.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Dr. Mahmoud stated that the patient came to the hospital in a serious condition suffering from hypertension and severe back and chest pains &ndash; so a medical team from different specialties was formed&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">First, the medical team decided to do a CT scan that showed a dissection in the descending aorta, the largest artery in the body that runs down through the chest and the abdomen.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">The team that was consisted of Dr. Elmeinesy, Dr.Samer Qara chief of ICU unit, Dr. Yasser Ghoneim cardiothoracic Consultant, and Dr. Syed Hassan Consultant Interventional Radiology- decided to perform a catheterization to deploy an aortic stent covered the main dissection entry point to prevent possible rupture and fatal bleeding</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">The operation was a success, and the patient was discharged in good health, noting that he will continue the follow-ups for six months to check his condition</p>','2021-01-03 11:29:03','2021-01-03 11:29:03'),(1773,'blogs','title',15,'en','COOLED RADIOFREQUENCY ABLATION MODALITY TO TREAT CHRONIC JOINTS PAIN','2021-01-03 11:31:44','2021-01-03 11:31:44'),(1774,'blogs','slug',15,'en','cooled-radiofrequency-ablation-modality-to-treat-chronic-joints-pain','2021-01-03 11:31:44','2021-01-03 11:31:44'),(1775,'blogs','content',15,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Cooled Radiofrequency Ablation Modality to Treat Chronic Joints Pain</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Many people around the world, especially the elderly, are suffering from chronic joints pain, chronic neck pain, and chronic back pain, especially when the surgery is not an option either because of the patient&rsquo;s age or because of having chronic diseases that prevent the patient from having the surgery.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">On the other hand, physicians attempt to offer optimal treatment that is appropriate for all these patients. Here at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, we strive to find innovative treatment solutions that can relieve pain without the need for surgical intervention.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">As the first of its kind on the regional level, the pain management team, led by Dr. Hesham Soliman, an anesthesia consultant and chief of anesthesia and pain management department, and Dr. Osama Al-Attiyah, an anesthesia and pain management consultant, succeed in treating a patient with chronic knee pain using the newest modality of pain management which called cooled radiofrequency ablation.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">What is the cooled radiofrequency ablation modality?</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">It is a minimally-invasive procedure used to treat chronic knee pain in 2-stpes approach:</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">First procedure, which is diagnostic: where the medication is injected into the nerves around the knee, which called the Genicular nerves.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;This medication serves to temporarily block the pain signals.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">The second step, which is the actual knee radiofrequency ablation</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">The Procedure is quite simple and easy. It is a day case procedure where a specialized needle is used to apply heat directly to the nerves of the knee. After this way, it is unable to continue sending pain signals to the brain. The pain relief from this procedure can last up to 2 years or more</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Special things of the cooled radiofrequency ablation that can help with chronic pain include: relieving pain, improving mobility, improving the long-term physical function and quality of life, it is quick to be done, quick recovery time, no overnight hospital stays, and no need for surgical incision.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Lastly, all thanks and appreciation to the pain management team and we wish the patient a good health.</p>','2021-01-03 11:31:44','2021-01-03 11:31:44'),(1776,'menu_items','title',52,'en','Moosa History','2021-01-03 13:41:47','2021-01-03 13:41:47'),(1779,'blogs','title',5,'en','‏OFFICE NANOSCOPE ثورة في علاج المفاصل بتقنية النانو سكوب بدون جراحة','2021-01-04 07:18:35','2021-01-04 07:18:35'),(1780,'blogs','slug',5,'en','office-nanoscope-thwrh-fy-alaj-almfasl-btqnyh-alnanw-skwb-bdwn-jrahh','2021-01-04 07:18:35','2021-01-04 07:18:35'),(1781,'blogs','content',5,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">يعتبر مفصل الكتف من أكثر المفاصل مرونة في جسم الإنسان حيث يسمح بأكبر قدر ممكن من الحركة للقيام بالأعمال والأنشطة اليومية. ولكن هذه المرونة تأتي على حساب ثبات المفصل واتزانه مما يجعله الأكثر عرضة للإصابة والخلع&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">خاصة عند الرياضيين. تتسبب مشكلات الكتف الناتجة عن هذه الإصابات في حدوث آلام شديدة ومزعجة، كما انها تؤدي الى تقييد حركة الكتف لفترات طويلة.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">وفي انجاز يعتبر الأول من نوعه على مستوى المملكة العربية السعودية، شهد مستشفى الموسى التخصصي بالأحساء نجاح أول عملية تنظير مفصلي باستخدام تقنية النانو سكوب Nanoscope Arthroscopy لمريض في العقد الثالث من العمر يعاني من انحشار وقطع جزئي لوتر الكتف المدورة.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">حيث كان المريض يشتكي من الام مزمنة في تلك المنطقة لمدة ثمانية أشهر تحد من حركته وتمنعه من ممارسة حياته الطبيعية. وأوضح الشاب أنه تم علاجه بالأدوية المسكنة ومضادات الالتهابات وجلسات العلاج الطبيعي ولم تتحسن حالته وأصبح التدخل الجراحي هو الحل الأمثل. وبعد اجراء الفحوصات اللازمة قرر الفريق الطبي بإجراء تنظير المفصل باستخدام تقنية النانو سكوب لإنهاء معاناة الشاب وتكللت العملية &ndash; بفضل الله- بالنجاح واسترجع المريض حركه الكتف بشكل جيد بعد العملية مباشرة.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">وبحسب الدكتور نايف الحمام، استشاري جراحة العظام والاصابات الرياضية بمستشفى الموسى التخصصي والذي أجري هذه العملية، إن هذه الطريقة عبارة عن اجراء جراحي حديث ونادر لتشخيص وعلاج امراض الكتف والركبة في نفس&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">الجلسة. حيث يتم الاعتماد في هذه التقنية على استخدام أجهزة وأدوات بأحجام صغيرة جدا &rdquo; بحجم الابرة&rdquo; ذات دقة عالية وتصاميم مبتكرة، وهذا بدوره يساهم في تشخيص وعلاج العديد من حالات العظام بشكل سريع وآمن وبتدخل جراحي أقل.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">يضيف الدكتور الحمام يتم خلال هذه العملية الحديثة عمل ثقب واحد&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">مصغر يتراوح بين ١.٥ الى ١.٩ مل تحت التخدير الموضعي في العيادة</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;ودو</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">ن الحاجة الى غرفة العمليات. يتم بعدها ادخال منظار المفصل للفحص والتشخيص باستخدام كاميرا عالية الجودة، وبمجرد الانتهاء من الفحص يتم اصلاح الاضرار في المفصل وعلاجها بتنظيف الأنسجة التالفة وإزالة النتوء العظمي البارز.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">بينما في جراحة التنظير المفصلي التقليدية -وهي لأكثر شيوعاً حاليا في علاج مثل هذه الحالات- يتم عمل عدة شقوق جراحية يتراوح طولهما ٤مل، أحدهمالمنظار المفصل والآخر للأدوات الجراحية ويخضع المريض خلالها لعملية التخدير العام أو الجزئي في غرفة العمليات في مدة تتراوح بين الساعة الى ساعتين ويحتاج بعدها المريض الى فترة تعافي تتراوح من ثلاث الى ستة أسابيع.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">كما أشاد الدكتور نايف الحمام بمميزات هذه التقنية، والتي يمكن وصفها بالثورة العلاجية في عالم جراحة العظام والطب الرياضي، موضحاً بأن مدة العملية تستغرق ما بين ١٠ الى ٣٠ دقيقة ويسمح للمريض بمغادرة المستشفى بعدها وممارسة الحياة الطبيعية والعودة للعمل. ومن مميزاتها أيضا عدم وجود الام ومعدل الاستشفاء فيها أسرع حيث ترجع حركة الكتف الى الحدود الطبيعية في نفس يوم العملية. كما أنها لا تحتاج الى غرز جراحية مما يقلل من حدوث المضاعفات الناتجة عن العملية. وأيضا تعتبر هذه التقنية البديل الأمثل لتصوير الرنين المغناطيسي خصوصا للحالات التي لا يجوز معها استخدام الرنين المغناطيسي، كما لو كان المريض يعاني من رهاب الأماكن المغلقة أو كان هناك اجسام معدنيه في الجسم المراد تصويره.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: an