 and bacterial infections of the bones.</p>\n<p>&bull; We provide the necessary rehabilitation to our patients as we take care of them by providing them with appropriate physical therapy services, to fully recover and return the affected organs to their normal state.</p>','2021-01-04 16:26:39','2021-03-08 19:01:10'),(1837,'service_section_items','title',107,'en','Orthopedic and joint and trauma surgeries','2021-01-04 16:27:40','2021-01-04 16:27:40'),(1838,'blogs','seo_title',15,'en','تقنية التردد الحراري المبرد لعلاج آلام المفاصل','2021-01-04 16:46:48','2021-01-04 16:46:48'),(1839,'blogs','meta_description',15,'en','تعتبر الآلام المزمنة للمفاصل والرقبة والظهر الهم الذي يرافق أغلب كبار السن، وخصوصا عندما لا تكون العملية الجراحية خيارًا متاحًا، إما بسبب كبر سن المريض أو وجود أمراض مزمنة تمنعه من إجراء العملية. فيظهر التردد الحراري كعلاج آمن وسريع أمام المرضى','2021-01-04 16:46:48','2021-01-04 16:46:48'),(1840,'blogs','meta_keywords',15,'en','العظام - المفاصل - التردد الحراري','2021-01-04 16:46:48','2021-01-04 16:46:48'),(1841,'data_rows','display_name',307,'en','Content2','2021-01-05 13:06:57','2021-01-05 13:06:57'),(1842,'data_rows','display_name',308,'en','Image2','2021-01-05 13:06:57','2021-01-05 13:06:57'),(1843,'services','content2',7,'en','<p>In the Neurosciences Center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, we offer you a model of an advanced and contemporary medical center, which contains a group of doctors of neurosciences and subspecialties. The center also contains advanced and modern medical devices, to provide you with an integrated treatment service that relieves your pain and soothes incurable diseases.</p>\n<p>The center consists of the Department of Neurosurgery, Spine Surgery, Neurology, Neurophysiology, Sleep Disorders Center, Psychiatry, and Psychology. Our services are distinguished by their combination of dedication and compassion, between expertise and competence, which would provide evidence-based care to meet all patients\' requests and provide them with comfort. We take care of their details and give them our greatest attention!</p>','2021-01-05 21:33:40','2021-03-11 13:13:26'),(1844,'services','content2',8,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The center is supervised by a group of consultants specializing in orthopedic medicine and surgery, who have the highest scientific degrees and who have extensive experience in the subspecialties of orthopedics and medicine.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The center also receives all orthopedic injuries that include car accidents, work injuries, sports injuries, and shoulder injuries through outpatient clinics, or through the emergency unit, that operates 24 hours.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The Sports Trauma Unit at Almoosa Specialist Hospital is one of the most important milestones in the field of health care for athletes in the Al-Ahsaa region.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2021-01-05 21:36:41','2021-03-11 13:13:08'),(1845,'services','content2',6,'en','<p>Being interested in the small details that make the Almoosa Specialist Hospital special, we gave the heart center within the hospital high importance, with an integrated medical team with extensive experience in the field of treating cardiothoracic diseases for adults and children.</p>\n<p>The center is equipped with the latest medical devices and medical innovations, proven and internationally approved scientific methods, and exceptional and unique capabilities in diagnosing and tracking cases of heart patients during surgical and non-surgical procedures or interventional catheters, which made our services within the Heart Center unique.</p>\n<p>Comprehensive services are provided by outpatient clinics to all cardiac patients who need a full assessment of their condition and permanent care, and non-invasive cardiac services are provided to adults and children. Using the latest medical devices such as ECHO, TEE, Magnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI) imaging, nuclear diagnostic imaging, and potentiometer, we diagnose the case without surgical intervention.</p>','2021-01-05 21:38:57','2021-03-11 13:14:08'),(1846,'pages','title',11,'en','Almoosa Specialist Hospital History','2021-01-05 22:09:07','2021-03-09 08:29:34'),(1847,'pages','slug',11,'en','moosa-history','2021-01-05 22:09:07','2021-01-05 22:09:07'),(1848,'pages','meta_description',11,'en','meta description','2021-01-05 22:09:07','2021-01-05 22:09:07'),(1849,'pages','meta_keywords',11,'en','meta keywords','2021-01-05 22:09:07','2021-01-05 22:09:07'),(1850,'pages','body',4,'en','<p>By downloading Almoosa Specialist Hospital Free Application, You can view your medical record, get monthly medication, and enjoy the electronic payment service at any time and from anywhere.</p>','2021-01-06 09:22:47','2021-03-11 12:52:18'),(1851,'services','excerpt',15,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The Nawal Al-Afaliq Cancer Center provides full treatment plans and full medical care for people with cancer.</span></p>','2021-01-06 20:17:30','2021-01-06 20:17:30'),(1852,'services','content2',28,'en','<p>We also aim to inform patients and help individuals to know risk factors and early signs of a stroke, and to contact KSA 997 immediately when any symptoms of stroke occur, in our belief in the role of the knowledge weapon in facing stroke, its symptoms, and complications.</p>\n<p>The program is supported by a multi-task team of different medical specialties and nurses available 24 hours a day, seven days a week, carefully qualified to diagnose stroke, rapidly and effectively administer treatment, control symptoms, and minimize complications to the greatest extent possible.</p>\n<p>In addition to our role in stroke treatment, the program provides a full range of outpatient neurology rehabilitation services, including speech problems, occupational therapy and physiotherapy services, in addition to continuous follow-up, high care, and ongoing patient advice, to take care of patients to the fullest.</p>','2021-01-06 20:46:36','2021-01-08 13:18:18'),(1853,'services','excerpt',26,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Diabetes is one of the fastest-growing health problems in the world, and the number of people with it has reached a very large percentage in Saudi Arabia.</span></p>','2021-01-06 20:50:57','2021-01-06 20:50:57'),(1854,'services','content2',26,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">At Al-Moosa Center for Diabetes and Endocrinology, we provide a multidisciplinary team made up of endocrinologists, ophthalmologists, cardiologists, diabetes experts, and a dietitian, all of whom work to provide patients with accurate diagnosis and effective treatment plans.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Our center is equipped with the latest technology for laboratory testing, blood sugar monitors, glucose sensors, and provides the latest diabetes treatments and medications.</span></p>','2021-01-06 20:50:57','2021-01-06 20:50:57'),(1855,'services','excerpt',25,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">In the Urology Unit at Al Moosa Specialist Hospital, we provide general care related to a wide and complex range of urinary problems.</span></p>','2021-01-06 20:52:03','2021-01-06 20:52:03'),(1856,'services','excerpt',24,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The Vascular Surgery Clinic at Al-Moosa Hospital provides diagnostic and treatment services for arterial and venous problems, some of which are done without surgical intervention using the laser, and the other is using surgery.</span></p>','2021-01-06 20:53:37','2021-01-06 20:53:37'),(1857,'services','excerpt',23,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Plastic surgery is one of the most important and widespread surgeries in our modern time, as the human being always seeks beauty and distinction by keeps up with the latest modern cosmetic technologies.</span></p>','2021-01-06 20:55:47','2021-01-06 20:55:47'),(1858,'services','excerpt',22,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The respiratory system is one of the basic organs in the human body, and diseases related to it are among the most common. By virtue of human life in the modern era, ambient air pollution, and the spread of radioactive materials.</span></p>','2021-01-06 20:57:13','2021-01-06 20:57:13'),(1859,'services','excerpt',21,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">In a healthcare system, that is getting more and more complex, caring for patients becomes difficult and limited. From here comes our role &ndash; we, the family medicine clinic - at Almoosa Specialist Hospital to provide integrated and continuous health care in which the focus is on the individual as a human being with his details that we take care of, with all his distinctive human makeup of spirit, mind, and body.</span></p>','2021-01-06 20:58:10','2021-03-11 13:10:30'),(1860,'services','excerpt',20,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The Dermatology Clinic at Al Moosa Specialist Hospital offers a wide range of curative and cosmetic services.</span></p>','2021-01-06 20:59:02','2021-01-06 20:59:02'),(1861,'services','excerpt',18,'en','<p>Children are the bright side in the life of parents; it is around them that the lives and concerns of the parents revolve around them. Therefore, the health of our children is a priority for the parents as it is our priority also in the pediatric center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital. The hospital is one of the most comprehensive care centers for children in the region</p>','2021-01-06 21:01:49','2021-03-11 13:11:04'),(1862,'services','excerpt',17,'en','<p>The Department of Kidney Diseases and Dialysis at Almoosa Specialist Hospital contains numerous modern medical devices related to the field.</p>\n<p>The most prominent of which is the (BBRAUN Dialog) devices, which are considered one of the best and most modern dialysis techniques in the world, as they are characterized by high efficiency, ease of use, and complete safety. They are also equipped with a large screen that monitors all indicators during the washing session, including the indicator for automatic blood pressure measurement.</p>','2021-01-06 21:06:38','2021-03-11 13:11:32'),(1863,'services','content2',17,'en','<p>It is also worth noting that the dialysis unit at Almoosa Hospital is one of the largest units in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, as it contains 30 dialysis machines with a capacity of 120 patients. Each patient has a unique space to ensure privacy and reduce the possibility of infection. The dialysis unit is based on a team of skilled consultants and specialists in nephrology and dialysis.</p>\n<p>We also have in the unit a professional technical staff and nurses who are fully trained in the field of dialysis. We strive to achieve the principle of comprehensive medical care that makes the patient the focus of his attention, and from here, we have provided the center with clinical dietitians and social workers who collaborate in one team.</p>\n<p>The team is tasked with making the rounds to provide patients with necessary information about their diet and to support them socially and psychologically. The hospital gives priority to hemodialysis patients, as it provides them with dedicated parking in the basement and provides them with private car transportation from their homes to the hospital for free.</p>\n<p>Finally, we hope that the dialysis unit, with its modern, advanced equipment and integrated staff, will be a distinctive mark and a qualitative addition in the field of dialysis patient care in the eastern region of the Kingdom.</p>','2021-01-06 21:06:38','2021-03-11 13:11:32'),(1864,'services','excerpt',16,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">In the Gastroenterology Center, we provide integrated medical care for patients, starting with the proper diagnosis of the situation and taking a history of it, through diagnosis using modern and advanced medical devices.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Then treatment according to organized, detailed, comprehensive treatment plans for the appropriate medication and appropriate medical intervention, in addition to periodic follow-up of the case continuously, leading to the patient\'s complete recovery and return to normal life.</span></p>','2021-01-06 21:07:29','2021-01-06 21:07:29'),(1865,'services','excerpt',14,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The emergency center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital is distinguished by providing various and integrated health services to satisfy the aspirations of its patients and achieve their aspirations.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Our center features specialized doctors who work around the clock, seven days a week, to serve patients and clients, assisted by the latest state-of-the-art medical technology in the field of emergency</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The Al-Mousa Emergency Center receives more than eighty-six thousand cases annually and includes several specialties such as internal medicine, cardiac services, obstetrics and gynecology, and general surgery.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">It has been provided with twenty-six beds and several rooms for unexpected deliveries, and a staff of the most skilled consultants and specialists in specialized clinics such as the pediatric clinic, the internal medicine clinic, the obstetrics and gynecology clinic, and general surgery, all operate around the clock.</span></p>','2021-01-06 21:09:42','2021-03-11 13:11:55'),(1866,'services','content2',14,'en','<p>Our staff is always in a state of maximum alert, reflecting the hospital&rsquo;s management&rsquo;s keenness to provide fast and accurate health service to save patients &rsquo;lives as quickly as possible with the help of modern medical devices with high accuracy in diagnosis, which helps in reaching the best results.</p>\n<p>Our consultants in the emergency center are always on standby, as soon as they are asked to attend; they will be in the hospital immediately. We have attracted in this center a medical staff with high experience and qualified nursing staff to work to the fullest.</p>\n<p>The center is characterized by its unique design, in which amenities are taken into account and the ease of access for patients to all places that may be needed in the fastest time, such as transferring critical cases to the care unit or operating rooms. Our center provides fast emergency services to the injured through ambulances equipped with the latest technologies in the field of emergency medicine to achieve high-quality medical service centered on patient comfort and health care.</p>','2021-01-06 21:09:42','2021-01-08 13:36:56'),(1867,'services','excerpt',13,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Sleep is acknowledged as one of the most important vital processes in the human body, which extends to four stages up to its final stage. Any defect or problem in one of these stages may lead to problems and disturbances, which negatively affect human health and productivity.</span></p>','2021-01-06 21:10:39','2021-01-06 21:10:39'),(1868,'services','excerpt',12,'en','<p>Surgery is one of the largest and most basic departments of medicine that requires a high degree of accuracy, competence and experience, by which it requires a thorough knowledge of organ anatomy and the correct method.</p>\n<p>Choosing the most appropriate surgical intervention based on the case information and applying it correctly without any errors or complications after the operation is a necessity and requires experience and competence.</p>','2021-01-06 21:12:15','2021-01-08 13:40:07'),(1869,'services','excerpt',11,'en','<p>At Almoosa Specialist Hospital, we care about women and take care of them, so we set up a special section for them on their health. We provide her with reliable medical advice in everything related to women\'s health, from infertility and reproduction problems or problems of menstruation, puberty, and growth, we take care of every detail of female safety through doctors with international accredited certificates from prestigious universities and excellent experience and competence, assisted by nursing staff with extensive experience and high competence in the field.</p>','2021-01-06 21:13:00','2021-03-11 13:12:37'),(1870,'services','excerpt',10,'en','<p>Obesity is considered a common disease of the age due to the change in the lifestyle of young people and children greatly, as they have become dependent on diets full of fat and carbohydrates and low in protein and fiber.</p>\n<p>The physical activity limited by the rule of long sitting on electronic devices and not practicing any kind of sport is a reason for this. This leads to the accumulation of fats in the tissues of the body and increases the incidence of cardiovascular disease and hardening of the arteries and death rates.</p>','2021-01-06 21:15:48','2021-01-08 13:44:04'),(1871,'services','content2',10,'en','<p>We, at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, and based on our medical and social responsibilities, have established a center for the treatment of obesity with a highly qualified medical and administrative staff and integrated medical knowledge and equipped with the latest medical devices in the treatment of obesity of all kinds.</p>\n<p>The causes and types of obesity differ, and with that, the methods of diagnosis and treatment are different. Therefore, because obesity treatment is a distinct medical subspecialty, we were keen at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital to establish an integrated medical team to reach an accurate medical diagnosis of the condition and thus a successful and effective treatment.</p>\n<p>The team is equipped with anesthesiologists, endocrinologists, psychiatrists, gastroenterologists, and other distinguished specialists, who work in operating rooms equipped with the latest medical devices in the field of stapling and endoscopy.</p>','2021-01-06 21:15:48','2021-01-08 13:44:04'),(1872,'services','excerpt',9,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The eye center within Almoosa Specialist Hospital is one of the best-advanced medical centers for eye treatment in the region in terms of efficiency, medical equipment, facilities, and services provided to patients.</span></p>','2021-01-06 21:16:56','2021-03-11 13:12:50'),(1873,'services','excerpt',8,'en','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The Orthopedic Center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital is one of the largest specialized centers in the area, which provides combined diagnostic and therapeutic services for all cases of bone, joint, and fracture diseases.</span></p>','2021-01-06 21:17:59','2021-03-11 13:13:08'),(1874,'services','excerpt',7,'en','<p>In the Neurosciences Center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, we offer you a model of an advanced and cont