n important goal of increasing the capacity of hospital beds to 100 to accommodate more patients through hospital buildings supported by all modern medical technology and equipment.</p>','2021-02-09 16:17:32','2021-02-09 16:17:32'),(2119,'histories','content',9,'en','<p>With the continuous expansion of the scale of the hospital, the Intensive Care Unit (ICU) has been opened and supported by a group of qualified medical staff to provide patients with high-quality care.</p>','2021-02-09 16:17:55','2021-02-09 16:17:55'),(2120,'histories','content',10,'en','<p>Al Moosa Hospital successfully established a radiology department and added MRI to its radiology services to ensure safety and accurate diagnosis for patients.</p>','2021-02-09 16:18:16','2021-02-09 16:18:16'),(2121,'histories','content',11,'en','<p>Until 2009, Al Moosa Hospital was accredited by the United International Committee for the Accreditation of Health Organizations (JCI), and adheres to the highest international standards of quality control, patient safety and best practices worldwide.</p>','2021-02-09 16:18:37','2021-02-09 16:18:37'),(2122,'histories','content',12,'en','<p>Hospital directors were interested in joining young, ambitious leaders, and providing them with all the means of support to help them in using their skills and talents to achieve the hospital\'s vision and desired goals.</p>','2021-02-09 16:19:00','2021-02-09 16:19:00'),(2123,'histories','content',13,'en','<p>Opening the LASIK and vision correction department at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, using the latest LASIK technologies and devices, to provide our patients with the safest and most accurate LASIK treatment.</p>','2021-02-09 16:20:46','2021-03-11 13:19:40'),(2124,'histories','content',14,'en','<p>Almoosa Specialist Hospital has been accredited for the second time by the Joint International Accreditation Committee (JCI), adhering to all local and international health quality regulations and procedures.</p>','2021-02-09 16:21:05','2021-03-11 13:19:28'),(2125,'histories','content',15,'en','<p>In 2013, the Al Moosa Specialist Hospital was accredited by the Saudi Central Board for Accreditation of Healthcare Institutions (CBAHI) - the official council that authorized accreditation to all healthcare facilities in Saudi Arabia.</p>','2021-02-09 16:21:29','2021-02-09 16:21:29'),(2126,'histories','content',16,'en','<ul>\n<li>Receiving the Award from Al-Ahsa Chamber of Commerce.</li>\n<li>Launching the New Identity.</li>\n<li>HACCP accreditation of Almoosa Specialist Hospital Nutrition and Food Services Department.</li>\n</ul>','2021-02-09 16:21:59','2021-03-11 13:18:59'),(2127,'histories','content',17,'en','<ul>\n<li>With the support of the most qualified medical professionals and the latest medical equipment, Almoosa Specialist Hospital Heart Center opened to provide safe medical services to patients\' hearts.</li>\n<li>Open a medical tower and increase its capacity to 240 beds.</li>\n<li>Planetree was awarded Almoosa Specialist Hospital&nbsp;Silver Award for its role in providing high-quality healthcare that meets all international standards.</li>\n</ul>','2021-02-09 16:22:59','2021-03-11 13:17:24'),(2128,'histories','content',18,'en','<ul>\n<li>Opening of &ldquo;Nawal Al-Afaliq&rdquo; oncology center. Opening of the digital surgery unit.</li>\n<li>Signing for the establishment of the North Tower.</li>\n<li>Signing for the development of the Hospital Information System</li>\n</ul>','2021-02-09 16:23:35','2021-02-09 16:23:35'),(2129,'histories','content',20,'en','<ul>\n<li>King Abdulaziz Quality Award.</li>\n<li>ASMBS accreditation - Bariatric Center of Excellence.</li>\n<li>Guinness world record.</li>\n<li>JCI accreditation for the 4the time.</li>\n</ul>','2021-02-09 16:25:18','2021-02-09 16:25:18'),(2130,'histories','content',21,'en','<ul>\n<li>The affiliation Agreement University of Chicago.</li>\n<li>American Association of blood banks (AABB).</li>\n<li>C.Everret Koop For Workplace Health Promotion Programs.</li>\n<li>HIMSS - Healthcare Information and Management Systems Society.</li>\n</ul>','2021-02-09 16:26:17','2021-02-09 16:26:17'),(2131,'histories','content',22,'en','<ul>\n<li>&ldquo;ACR&rdquo; CT Scan accreditation ensures that our hospital meets the international standards for imaging quality and safety.</li>\n<li>Starting our journey to Magnet, the gold standard given to hospitals for quality patient care, nursing excellence, and innovations in professional nursing practice.</li>\n</ul>','2021-02-09 16:27:59','2021-02-09 16:27:59'),(2132,'history_heads','title',6,'en','Transition and Success','2021-02-09 16:29:07','2021-02-09 16:29:07'),(2133,'history_heads','description',6,'en','<p>This is the transitional and successful phase for Al Moosa Specialist Hospital, after a long journey of hard work to provide the highest quality of medical services.</p>','2021-02-09 16:29:07','2021-02-09 16:29:07'),(2134,'history_heads','title',5,'en','Excellence and Innovation','2021-02-09 16:32:50','2021-02-09 16:32:50'),(2135,'history_heads','description',5,'en','<p>Our hospital has completed its certification path of health excellence and the massive expansion of the medical tower and opening of new medical centers to serve the community in all health aspects and specializations.</p>','2021-02-09 16:32:50','2021-02-09 16:32:50'),(2136,'history_heads','title',4,'en','Development and Accreditations','2021-02-09 16:33:27','2021-02-09 16:33:27'),(2137,'history_heads','description',4,'en','<p>At this stage, the hospital has grown significantly in addition to the accreditation certificates and awards in recognition of our hospital\'s efforts to improve the healthcare system in Al-Ahsa city.</p>','2021-02-09 16:33:27','2021-02-09 16:33:27'),(2138,'history_heads','title',3,'en','Hospital Expansion','2021-02-09 16:34:27','2021-02-09 16:34:27'),(2139,'history_heads','description',3,'en','<p>By the early 2000s, Al-Moosa Hospital rapidly expanded to provide safe healthcare s